                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_nh'),           n.today_payments_nh, o.today_payments_nh) AS today_payments_nh,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_lotte'),        n.today_payments_lotte, o.today_payments_lotte) AS today_payments_lotte,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_baemin'),       n.today_payments_baemin, o.today_payments_baemin) AS today_payments_baemin,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_bc'),           n.today_payments_bc, o.today_payments_bc) AS today_payments_bc,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_samsung'),      n.today_payments_samsung, o.today_payments_samsung) AS today_payments_samsung,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_shinhan'),      n.today_payments_shinhan, o.today_payments_shinhan) AS today_payments_shinhan,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_hana'),         n.today_payments_hana, o.today_payments_hana) AS today_payments_hana,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_hyundai'),      n.today_payments_hyundai, o.today_payments_hyundai) AS today_payments_hyundai,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_yogiyo'),       n.today_payments_yogiyo, o.today_payments_yogiyo) AS today_payments_yogiyo,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_baedaltong'),   n.today_payments_baedaltong, o.today_payments_baedaltong) AS today_payments_baedaltong,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'delivery_app_sales_baemin_amount'),        n.delivery_app_sales_baemin_amount, o.delivery_app_sales_baemin_amount) AS delivery_app_sales_baemin_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'delivery_app_sales_yogiyo_amount'),        n.delivery_app_sales_yogiyo_amount, o.delivery_app_sales_yogiyo_amount) AS delivery_app_sales_yogiyo_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'delivery_app_sales_baedaltong_amount'),    n.delivery_app_sales_baedaltong_amount, o.delivery_app_sales_baedaltong_amount) AS delivery_app_sales_baedaltong_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'delivery_app_sales_monthly_amount'),       n.delivery_app_sales_monthly_amount, o.delivery_app_sales_monthly_amount) AS delivery_app_sales_monthly_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'card_purchases_monthly_amount'),           n.card_purchases_monthly_amount, o.card_purchases_monthly_amount) AS card_purchases_monthly_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'hometax_sales_monthly_invoice_amount'),    n.hometax_sales_monthly_invoice_amount, o.hometax_sales_monthly_invoice_amount) AS hometax_sales_monthly_invoice_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'hometax_sales_monthly_cash_amount'),       n.hometax_sales_monthly_cash_amount, o.hometax_sales_monthly_cash_amount) AS hometax_sales_monthly_cash_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'hometax_purchases_monthly_cash_amount'),   n.hometax_purchases_monthly_cash_amount, o.hometax_purchases_monthly_cash_amount) AS hometax_purchases_monthly_cash_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount'),n.hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount, o.hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount) AS hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount,
                  o.hourly_sales_etc_amount,
                  o.future_payments_arr,
                  o.bank_accounts_arr,
                  o.today_card_purchases_arr
        FROM      formatted_report_logs AS o
        LEFT OUTER JOIN   formatted_daily_report AS n
        ON        o.business_id = n.business_id
)
)

SELECT    *,
          date_format('2021-01-01', 'M월') AS report_month,
          date_format('2021-01-01', 'M월 d일') AS report_date,
          dayofweek_kor('2021-01-01') AS report_day_of_week,
          date_format('2021-01-02', 'M월 d일') AS today_date,
          dayofweek_kor('2021-01-02') AS today_day_of_week,

          IF(bank_account_etc_count > 0, true, false) AS bank_account_etc_exists,
          IF(today_card_purchases_etc_count > 0, true, false) AS today_card_purchases_etc_exists,
          IF(size(delivery_app_sales) > 0, true, false) AS delivery_app_sales_exists,
          IF(size(today_payments) > 0, true, false) AS today_payments_exists,
          IF(size(future_payments) > 0, true, false) AS future_payments_exists
FROM (
        SELECT    target_id, business_id, user_id, title, template_code, url_mobile,

                  FORMAT_NUMBER(card_sales_amount, 0) AS card_sales_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(card_sales_count, 0) AS card_sales_count,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(card_sales_fee, 0) AS card_sales_fee,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(card_sales_vat_fee, 0) AS card_sales_vat_fee,
                  IF(card_sales_vat_fee > 0, true, false) AS card_sales_vat_fee_exists,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(card_sales_payment, 0) AS card_sales_payment,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(card_sales_new_amount, 0) AS card_sales_new_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(card_sales_returning_amount, 0) AS card_sales_returning_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(card_sales_monthly_amount, 0) AS card_sales_monthly_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(delivery_app_sales_monthly_amount, 0) AS delivery_app_sales_monthly_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(card_purchases_monthly_amount, 0) AS card_purchases_monthly_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hometax_sales_monthly_invoice_amount, 0) AS hometax_sales_monthly_invoice_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hometax_sales_monthly_cash_amount, 0) AS hometax_sales_monthly_cash_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hometax_purchases_monthly_cash_amount, 0) AS hometax_purchases_monthly_cash_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount, 0) AS hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount,

                  NVL(FORMAT_NUMBER(FLOOR(card_sales_amount / card_sales_count), 0), '0') AS card_sales_unit_price,
                  NVL(FORMAT_NUMBER(ROUND(card_sales_new_amount / card_sales_amount * 100), 0), '0') AS card_sales_new_amount_percent,
                  NVL(FORMAT_NUMBER(ROUND(card_sales_returning_amount / card_sales_amount * 100), 0), '0') AS card_sales_returning_amount_percent,
                  IF(card_sales_amount > 0, true, false) AS card_sales_amount_exists,

                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hourly_sales_0_6_amount, 0) AS hourly_sales_0_6_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hourly_sales_6_11_amount, 0) AS hourly_sales_6_11_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hourly_sales_11_14_amount, 0) AS hourly_sales_11_14_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hourly_sales_14_17_amount, 0) AS hourly_sales_14_17_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hourly_sales_17_24_amount, 0) AS hourly_sales_17_24_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hourly_sales_etc_amount, 0) AS hourly_sales_etc_amount,
                  NVL(FORMAT_NUMBER(ROUND(hourly_sales_0_6_amount / hourly_sales_amount_sum * 100), 0), '0') AS hourly_sales_0_6_amount_percent,
                  NVL(FORMAT_NUMBER(ROUND(hourly_sales_6_11_amount / hourly_sales_amount_sum * 100), 0), '0') AS hourly_sales_6_11_amount_percent,
                  NVL(FORMAT_NUMBER(ROUND(hourly_sales_11_14_amount / hourly_sales_amount_sum * 100), 0), '0') AS hourly_sales_11_14_amount_percent,
                  NVL(FORMAT_NUMBER(ROUND(hourly_sales_14_17_amount / hourly_sales_amount_sum * 100), 0), '0') AS hourly_sales_14_17_amount_percent,
                  NVL(FORMAT_NUMBER(ROUND(hourly_sales_17_24_amount / hourly_sales_amount_sum * 100), 0), '0') AS hourly_sales_17_24_amount_percent,
                  NVL(FORMAT_NUMBER(ROUND(hourly_sales_etc_amount / hourly_sales_amount_sum * 100), 0), '0') AS hourly_sales_etc_amount_percent,
                  IF(hourly_sales_etc_amount > 0, true, false) AS hourly_sales_etc_amount_exists,
                  IF(hourly_sales_amount_sum > 0, true, false) AS hourly_sales_exists,

                  FORMAT_NUMBER(delivery_app_sales_baemin_amount, 0) AS delivery_app_sales_baemin_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(delivery_app_sales_yogiyo_amount, 0) AS delivery_app_sales_yogiyo_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(delivery_app_sales_baedaltong_amount, 0) AS delivery_app_sales_baedaltong_amount,

                  filter(today_payments_arr, d -> d.amount > 0) AS today_payments,
                  aggregate(today_payments_arr, 0L, (acc, d) -> acc + d.amount) AS today_payments_sum_amount,

                  future_payments_arr AS future_payments,
                  aggregate(future_payments_arr, 0L, (acc, d) -> acc + d.amount) AS future_payments_sum_amount,

                  slice(bank_accounts_arr, 1, 5) AS bank_accounts,
                  IF(size(bank_accounts_arr) > 5, size(bank_accounts_arr) - 5, 0) AS bank_account_etc_count,

                  slice(today_card_purchases_arr, 1, 5) AS today_card_purchases,
                  IF(size(today_card_purchases_arr) > 5, size(today_card_purchases_arr) - 5, 0) AS today_card_purchases_etc_count,

                  filter(delivery_app_sales_arr, d -> d.amount > 0) AS delivery_app_sales,

                  (
                      card_sales_monthly_amount +
                      delivery_app_sales_monthly_amount +
                      hometax_sales_monthly_invoice_amount +
                      hometax_sales_monthly_cash_amount
                  ) AS monthly_sales_sum,
                  (
                      card_purchases_monthly_amount +
                      hometax_purchases_monthly_cash_amount +
                      hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount
                  ) AS monthly_purchases_sum
        FROM      merged
)

SELECT 'campaign_id' AS id_type, id, name, CAST(null AS STRING) AS type, CAST(null AS INT) AS population FROM campaign
UNION ALL
SELECT 'ad_group_id' AS id_type, id, name, type, population FROM ad_group
UNION ALL
SELECT 'creative_id' AS id_type, id, name, message_type AS type, CAST(null AS INT) AS population FROM creative

SELECT id_type, id, campaign_id, ad_group_id, creative_id, status,
        min(timestamp) AS min_ts, max(timestamp) AS max_ts,
        count(1) AS send_cnt,
        count(distinct(user_id)) AS send_user_cnt
FROM (
    SELECT meta.*, status, user_id, timestamp
    FROM (
        SELECT  explode(meta_arr) AS meta, status, user_id, timestamp
        FROM (
                SELECT  array(
                            named_struct('id_type', 'campaign_id', 'id', campaign_id, 'campaign_id', campaign_id, 'ad_group_id', 'n/a', 'creative_id', 'n/a'),
                            named_struct('id_type', 'ad_group_id', 'id', ad_group_id, 'campaign_id', campaign_id, 'ad_group_id', ad_group_id, 'creative_id', 'n/a'),
                            named_struct('id_type', 'creative_id', 'id', creative_id, 'campaign_id', campaign_id, 'ad_group_id', ad_group_id, 'creative_id', creative_id)
                        ) AS meta_arr,
                        status, user_id, timestamp,
                        row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY _event_id ORDER BY timestamp DESC) AS rank
                FROM send_log
                WHERE created_at_date between '2020-01-01' AND '2021-01-14'
        )
        WHERE rank = 1
    )
)
GROUP BY  id_type, id, campaign_id, ad_group_id, creative_id, status

SELECT id_type, id, campaign_id, ad_group_id, creative_id, status,
        min(timestamp) AS min_ts, max(timestamp) AS max_ts,
        count(1) AS send_cnt,
        count(distinct(user_id)) AS send_user_cnt
FROM (
    SELECT meta.*, status, user_id, timestamp
    FROM (
        SELECT  explode(meta_arr) AS meta, status, user_id, timestamp
        FROM (
                SELECT  array(
                            named_struct('id_type', 'campaign_id', 'id', campaign_id, 'campaign_id', campaign_id, 'ad_group_id', 'n/a', 'creative_id', 'n/a'),
                            named_struct('id_type', 'ad_group_id', 'id', ad_group_id, 'campaign_id', campaign_id, 'ad_group_id', ad_group_id, 'creative_id', 'n/a'),
                            named_struct('id_type', 'creative_id', 'id', creative_id, 'campaign_id', campaign_id, 'ad_group_id', ad_group_id, 'creative_id', creative_id)
                        ) AS meta_arr,
                        status, user_id, timestamp,
                        row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY _event_id ORDER BY timestamp DESC) AS rank
                FROM send_log
                WHERE created_at_date between '2020-01-01' AND '2021-01-16'
        )
        WHERE rank = 1
    )
)
GROUP BY  id_type, id, campaign_id, ad_group_id, creative_id, status

SELECT
        id_type, id, campaign_id, ad_group_id, creative_id,
        IF(success_min_ts < fail_min_ts, success_min_ts, fail_min_ts) AS min_ts,
        IF(success_max_ts > fail_max_ts, success_max_ts, fail_max_ts) AS max_ts,
        success_send_cnt, success_send_user_cnt, fail_send_cnt, fail_send_user_cnt
FROM (
    SELECT
            nvl(success_log.id_type, fail_log.id_type) AS id_type,
            nvl(success_log.id, fail_log.id) AS id,
            nvl(success_log.campaign_id, fail_log.campaign_id) AS campaign_id,
            nvl(success_log.ad_group_id, fail_log.ad_group_id) AS ad_group_id,
            nvl(success_log.creative_id, fail_log.creative_id) AS creative_id,
            nvl(fail_log.min_ts, unix_timestamp()* 1000) AS fail_min_ts,
            nvl(success_log.min_ts, unix_timestamp()* 1000) AS success_min_ts,
            nvl(fail_log.max_ts, 0L) AS fail_max_ts,
            nvl(success_log.max_ts, 0L) AS success_max_ts,
            nvl(success_log.send_cnt, 0L) AS success_send_cnt,
            nvl(success_log.send_user_cnt, 0L) AS success_send_user_cnt,
            nvl(fail_log.send_cnt, 0L) AS fail_send_cnt,
            nvl(fail_log.send_user_cnt, 0L) AS fail_send_user_cnt
    FROM (
        SELECT *
        FROM send_log_by_status
        WHERE status = true
    ) AS success_log
    FULL OUTER JOIN
    (
        SELECT *
        FROM send_log_by_status
        WHERE status = false
    ) AS fail_log
    ON success_log.id_type = fail_log.id_type
    AND success_log.id = fail_log.id
)

SELECT
        id_type, id, campaign_id, ad_group_id, creative_id,
        IF(success_min_ts < fail_min_ts, success_min_ts, fail_min_ts) AS min_ts,
        IF(success_max_ts > fail_max_ts, success_max_ts, fail_max_ts) AS max_ts,
        success_send_cnt, success_send_user_cnt, fail_send_cnt, fail_send_user_cnt
FROM (
    SELECT
            nvl(success_log.id_type, fail_log.id_type) AS id_type,
            nvl(success_log.id, fail_log.id) AS id,
            nvl(success_log.campaign_id, fail_log.campaign_id) AS campaign_id,
            nvl(success_log.ad_group_id, fail_log.ad_group_id) AS ad_group_id,
            nvl(success_log.creative_id, fail_log.creative_id) AS creative_id,
            nvl(fail_log.min_ts, unix_timestamp()* 1000) AS fail_min_ts,
            nvl(success_log.min_ts, unix_timestamp()* 1000) AS success_min_ts,
            nvl(fail_log.max_ts, 0L) AS fail_max_ts,
            nvl(success_log.max_ts, 0L) AS success_max_ts,
            nvl(success_log.send_cnt, 0L) AS success_send_cnt,
            nvl(success_log.send_user_cnt, 0L) AS success_send_user_cnt,
            nvl(fail_log.send_cnt, 0L) AS fail_send_cnt,
            nvl(fail_log.send_user_cnt, 0L) AS fail_send_user_cnt
    FROM (
        SELECT *
        FROM send_log_by_status
        WHERE status = true
    ) AS success_log
    FULL OUTER JOIN
    (
        SELECT *
        FROM send_log_by_status
        WHERE status = false
    ) AS fail_log
    ON success_log.id_type = fail_log.id_type
    AND success_log.id = fail_log.id
)

SELECT
           id_type, id, campaign_id, ad_group_id, creative_id, min_ts, max_ts,
           success_send_cnt, success_send_user_cnt, fail_send_cnt, fail_send_user_cnt,
           click_cnt, click_user_cnt,
           start_time, end_time, diff_seconds,
           send_fail_rate, click_count_rate,
           hours, minutes, seconds,
           name, type, population
FROM (
        SELECT  *,
                floor(diff_seconds / 3600) AS hours,
                floor((diff_seconds % 3600) / 60) AS minutes,
                floor(diff_seconds % 60) AS seconds
        FROM (
            SELECT *,
                    date_format(from_utc_timestamp(from_unixtime(min_ts / 1000), 'Asia/Seoul'), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss') AS start_time,
                    date_format(from_utc_timestamp(from_unixtime(max_ts / 1000), 'Asia/Seoul'), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss') AS end_time,
                    ((max_ts - min_ts) / 1000) AS diff_seconds,
                    CAST(FORMAT_NUMBER(nvl(fail_send_cnt / success_send_cnt * 100, 0), '########.##') AS DOUBLE) AS send_fail_rate,
                    CAST(FORMAT_NUMBER(nvl(click_cnt / success_send_cnt * 100, 0), '########.##') AS DOUBLE) AS click_count_rate,
                    CAST(FORMAT_NUMBER(nvl(click_user_cnt / success_send_user_cnt * 100, 0), '########.##') AS DOUBLE) AS click_user_rate
            FROM   current_stat
        )
)

SELECT    acquirer_name,
          amount,
          row_number() OVER (
              PARTITION BY business_id, credential_key, CAST(transacted_at AS DATE), masked_card_number, authorization_number, amount, status
              ORDER BY created_at DESC
          ) AS approval_seq,
          authorization_number,
          business_id,
          card_number,
          card_type,
          credential_key,
          encrypted_card_number,
          estimated_fee AS fee,
          estimated_paid_at,
          installment,
          issuer_name,
          masked_card_number,
          merchant_number,
          amount - estimated_fee - estimated_vat_fee AS payment,
          scraping_type,
          status,
          transacted_at,
          NULLIF(estimated_vat_fee, 0) AS vat_fee,
          created_at,
          updated_at,
          created_at_date
FROM      (
    SELECT    a.*,
              estimate_paid_at(
                  a.issuer_name,
                  c.bank_name,
                  a.transacted_at,
                  COALESCE(c.calculated_purchase_period, 1),
                  COALESCE(c.calculated_payment_period, c.payment_period),
                  c.paid_on_weekends
              ) AS estimated_paid_at,
              CASE
                  WHEN card_type = 1 THEN
                      CAST((a.amount * COALESCE(c.calculated_credit_fee_rate, c.credit_fee_rate) / 100) AS INTEGER)
                  ELSE
                      CAST((a.amount * COALESCE(c.calculated_check_fee_rate, c.check_fee_rate_c) / 100) AS INTEGER)
              END AS estimated_fee,
              CASE
                  WHEN b.vat_withheld AND a.transacted_at > '2019-01-01' THEN
                      CAST((a.amount * 4 / 110 / 10) AS INTEGER) * 10
                  ELSE
                      0
              END AS estimated_vat_fee
    FROM      current_approvals a, businesses b, card_merchants c
    WHERE     a.business_id = b.id
    AND       a.business_id = c.business_id
    AND       a.issuer_name = c.issuer_name
    AND       a.merchant_number = c.merchant_number
)

SELECT
        business_id, duration, prev_duration,
        struct(
            amount_sum,
            amount_avg,
            tx_count_sum,
            tx_count_avg,
            unit_price
        ) AS metrics
FROM (
        SELECT
                business_id,
                dateRange.code AS duration,
                dateRange.prevCode AS prev_duration,
                amount_sum,
                ROUND(amount_sum / cnt) AS amount_avg,
                tx_count_sum,
                ROUND(tx_count_sum / cnt) AS tx_count_avg,
                ROUND(amount_sum / tx_count_sum) AS unit_price
        FROM (
            SELECT
                    business_id, dateRange,
                    SUM(amount) AS amount_sum,
                    SUM(tx_count) AS tx_count_sum,
                    count(1) AS cnt
            FROM (
                SELECT
                    business_id,
                    explode(dateRangeCodes) AS dateRange,
                    amount_sum AS amount,
                    tx_count
                FROM (
                    SELECT
                        business_id,
                        dateRangeCode(timestamp) AS dateRangeCodes,
                        amount_sum,
                        tx_count
                    FROM card_sales_transactions
                )
                WHERE size(dateRangeCodes) > 0
            )
            GROUP BY business_id, dateRange
        )
)

SELECT
            struct(bdong_range.*) AS depth3_range,
            struct(sigungu_range.*) AS depth2_range,
            struct(sido_range.*) AS depth1_range
    FROM  sido_range
    JOIN sigungu_range
    ON sido_range.sido_code = sigungu_range.sido_code
    AND sido_range.duration = sigungu_range.duration
    JOIN bdong_range
    ON sigungu_range.sido_code = bdong_range.sido_code
    AND  sigungu_range.sigungu_code = bdong_range.sigungu_code
    AND sigungu_range.duration = bdong_range.duration

SELECT
        business_id,
        name,
        location,
        kcd_classification,
        address,
        duration,
        metrics,
        prev_metrics,
        named_struct(
            'depth1', amount_range_depth1,
            'depth2', amount_range_depth2,
            'depth3', amount_range_depth3
        ) AS amount_range
FROM (
        SELECT
                business_meta_with_amount.*,
                CASE
                    WHEN metrics.amount_avg < depth1_range.amount_range[0] THEN "lower"
                    WHEN metrics.amount_avg < depth1_range.amount_range[1] THEN "lower_middle"
                    WHEN metrics.amount_avg < depth1_range.amount_range[2] THEN "upper_middle"
                    WHEN metrics.amount_avg >= depth1_range.amount_range[2] THEN "upper"
                    ELSE null
                END AS amount_range_depth1,
                CASE
                    WHEN metrics.amount_avg < depth2_range.amount_range[0] THEN "lower"
                    WHEN metrics.amount_avg < depth2_range.amount_range[1] THEN "lower_middle"
                    WHEN metrics.amount_avg < depth2_range.amount_range[2] THEN "upper_middle"
                    WHEN metrics.amount_avg >= depth2_range.amount_range[2] THEN "upper"
                    ELSE null
                END AS amount_range_depth2,
                CASE
                    WHEN metrics.amount_avg < depth3_range.amount_range[0] THEN "lower"
                    WHEN metrics.amount_avg < depth3_range.amount_range[1] THEN "lower_middle"
                    WHEN metrics.amount_avg < depth3_range.amount_range[2] THEN "upper_middle"
                    WHEN metrics.amount_avg >= depth3_range.amount_range[2] THEN "upper"
                    ELSE null
                END AS amount_range_depth3
        FROM business_meta_with_amount
        LEFT OUTER JOIN address_amount_range
        ON  business_meta_with_amount.duration = address_amount_range.depth3_range.duration
        AND business_meta_with_amount.address.sido_code = address_amount_range.depth3_range.sido_code
        AND business_meta_with_amount.address.sigungu_code = address_amount_range.depth3_range.sigungu_code
        AND business_meta_with_amount.address.b_code = address_amount_range.depth3_range.b_code
)

              '_label_name', label_name,
              '_timestamp', timestamp,

  AND

  AND
          label_name IS NOT null
)

SELECT    *
FROM (
        SELECT
                  nvl(snowdon.registration_number, goose.registration_number) AS registration_number,
                  'shinhan' AS card_issuer,
                  nvl(snowdon.classification_code, goose.classification_code) AS classification_code,
                  nvl(snowdon.classification_name, goose.classification_name) AS classification_name
        FROM (
                SELECT
                          card_classification.registration_number,
                          card_classification.card_issuer,
                          card_classification.classification_code,
                          shinhancard_classification.classification_name
                FROM  (
                          SELECT  *
                          FROM    card_payments_classification
                          WHERE   card_issuer = 'shinhan'
                ) card_classification
                LEFT OUTER JOIN   shinhancard_classification
                ON    card_classification.classification_code = shinhancard_classification.classification_code
        ) goose
        FULL OUTER JOIN (
          SELECT  *
          FROM (
                SELECT    registration_number, classification_code, classification_name,
                          row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY registration_number ORDER BY updated_at DESC) AS rank
                FROM      shinhancard_businesses
          )
          WHERE rank = 1
        ) snowdon
        ON    goose.registration_number = snowdon.registration_number
)
WHERE  classification_code IS NOT NULL

        hometax_classification_code AS code,
        hometax_classification_code_1_depth AS depth_1_code,
        hometax_classification_name_1_depth AS depth_1_name,
        hometax_classification_code_2_depth AS depth_2_code,
        hometax_classification_name_2_depth AS depth_2_name,
        hometax_classification_code_3_depth AS depth_3_code,
        hometax_classification_name_3_depth AS depth_3_name,
        hometax_classification_code_4_depth AS depth_4_code,
        hometax_classification_name_4_depth AS depth_4_name,
        hometax_classification_name_5_depth AS depth_5_name
FROM businesses
JOIN (
        SELECT *
        FROM (
                SELECT    *,
                          row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY hometax_classification_code ORDER BY id) AS code_rank
                FROM      hometax_ksic_map
        )
        WHERE code_rank = 1
) AS dedup_map
ON businesses.hometax_business_classification_code = dedup_map.hometax_classification_code

SELECT
          businesses.id AS business_id,
          businesses.registration_number,
          code,
          depth_1_code,
          depth_1_name,
          depth_2_code,
          depth_2_name,
          depth_3_code,
          depth_3_name,
          depth_4_code,
          depth_4_name,
          depth_5_name,
          depth_all,
          depth_1_2_code
FROM      businesses
JOIN (
      SELECT
              hometax_classification_code,
              collect_set(standard_classification_code) AS code,
              collect_set(standard_classification_code_1_depth) AS depth_1_code,
              collect_set(standard_classification_name_1_depth) AS depth_1_name,
              collect_set(standard_classification_code_2_depth) AS depth_2_code,
              collect_set(standard_classification_name_2_depth) AS depth_2_name,
              collect_set(standard_classification_code_3_depth) AS depth_3_code,
              collect_set(standard_classification_name_3_depth) AS depth_3_name,
              collect_set(standard_classification_code_4_depth) AS depth_4_code,
              collect_set(standard_classification_name_4_depth) AS depth_4_name,
              collect_set(standard_classification_name_5_depth) AS depth_5_name,
              to_json(
                  collect_set(
                      named_struct(
                          'depth_1_code', standard_classification_code_1_depth,
                          'depth_1_name', standard_classification_name_1_depth,
                          'depth_2_code', standard_classification_code_2_depth,
                          'depth_2_name', standard_classification_name_2_depth,
                          'depth_3_code', standard_classification_code_3_depth,
                          'depth_3_name', standard_classification_name_3_depth,
                          'depth_4_code', standard_classification_code_4_depth,
                          'depth_4_name', standard_classification_name_4_depth,
                          'depth_5_name', standard_classification_name_5_depth
                      )
                  )
              ) AS depth_all,
              collect_set(concat(standard_classification_code_1_depth,standard_classification_code_2_depth)) AS depth_1_2_code
      FROM    hometax_ksic_map
      GROUP BY hometax_classification_code
) AS ksic
ON businesses.hometax_business_classification_code = ksic.hometax_classification_code

SELECT   *

 WHERE    created_at_date >= '2019-12-22'

SELECT  business_id,
          amount_sum,
          fromYear, toYear,
          year_cnt,
          (amount_sum / year_cnt) AS amount_avg
  FROM (
      SELECT
               sales.business_id,
               sales.amount_sum,
               sales.year_cnt,
               CAST(YEAR(opend_at) AS INT) AS fromYear,
               CAST(YEAR(current_date()) AS INT) AS toYear
      FROM (
          SELECT business_id, SUM(amount) AS amount_sum, COUNT(DISTINCT YEAR(date)) AS year_cnt
          FROM hometax_sales_declarations
          WHERE form_type = '부가가치세신고서'
          GROUP BY business_id
      ) sales
      JOIN (
          SELECT business_id, opend_at
          FROM (
              SELECT business_id, taxation_type, to_date(opened_at, 'yyyyMMdd') AS opend_at
              FROM hometax_businesses
          )
          WHERE opend_at > '2015-12-31' AND opend_at < '2019-01-01'
          AND taxation_type != '간이과세자'
      ) valid_businesses
      ON sales.business_id = valid_businesses.business_id
  )

SELECT
          w.business_id,
          w.imputed_at,
          CASE
              WHEN declare_period = '반기' THEN fulltime_employees_count * 6
              ELSE fulltime_employees_count
          END AS fulltime_employees_count
  FROM hometax_wht_declarations w
  JOIN (
      SELECT business_id, imputed_at, max(declared_at) AS declared_at
      FROM  hometax_wht_declarations
      GROUP BY business_id, imputed_at
  ) AS latest_wht
  ON w.business_id = latest_wht.business_id
  AND w.imputed_at = latest_wht.imputed_at
  AND w.declared_at = latest_wht.declared_at

SELECT
          business_id,
          opend_at,
          CASE
              WHEN opend_at < '2019-01-01' THEN '2019-01-01'
              WHEN date_trunc('MONTH', opend_at) <= date_trunc('MONTH', add_months(current_date(), -12)) THEN date_trunc('MONTH', add_months(current_date(), -12))
              ELSE  date_trunc('MONTH', opend_at)
          END AS from_date,
          CASE
              WHEN opend_at < '2019-01-01' THEN '2020-01-01'
              ELSE  date_trunc('MONTH', current_date())
          END AS to_date

  FROM (
      SELECT business_id, to_date(opened_at, 'yyyyMMdd') AS opend_at
      FROM hometax_businesses
  )

SELECT
         wht.business_id,
         from_date, to_date,
         SUM(fulltime_employees_count) AS employ_count,
         ceil(months_between(to_date, from_date)) AS month_cnt,
         CAST(
             format_number(SUM(fulltime_employees_count) / ceil(months_between(to_date, from_date)), 2)
             AS DOUBLE
         ) AS employ_avg
FROM     wht
JOIN     businesses
ON wht.business_id = businesses.business_id
WHERE wht.imputed_at >= from_date AND  wht.imputed_at < to_date
GROUP BY wht.business_id, opend_at, from_date, to_date

SELECT 'campaign_id' AS id_type, id, name, CAST(null AS STRING) AS type, CAST(null AS INT) AS population FROM campaign
UNION ALL
SELECT 'ad_group_id' AS id_type, id, name, type, population FROM ad_group
UNION ALL
SELECT 'creative_id' AS id_type, id, name, message_type AS type, CAST(null AS INT) AS population FROM creative

SELECT id_type, id, campaign_id, ad_group_id, creative_id, status,
        min(timestamp) AS min_ts, max(timestamp) AS max_ts,
        count(1) AS send_cnt,
        count(distinct(user_id)) AS send_user_cnt
FROM (
    SELECT meta.*, status, user_id, timestamp
    FROM (
        SELECT  explode(meta_arr) AS meta, status, user_id, timestamp
        FROM (
                SELECT  array(
                            named_struct('id_type', 'campaign_id', 'id', campaign_id, 'campaign_id', campaign_id, 'ad_group_id', 'n/a', 'creative_id', 'n/a'),
                            named_struct('id_type', 'ad_group_id', 'id', ad_group_id, 'campaign_id', campaign_id, 'ad_group_id', ad_group_id, 'creative_id', 'n/a'),
                            named_struct('id_type', 'creative_id', 'id', creative_id, 'campaign_id', campaign_id, 'ad_group_id', ad_group_id, 'creative_id', creative_id)
                        ) AS meta_arr,
                        status, user_id, timestamp,
                        row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY _event_id ORDER BY timestamp DESC) AS rank
                FROM send_log
                WHERE created_at_date = '2021-01-29'
        )
        WHERE rank = 1
    )
)
GROUP BY  id_type, id, campaign_id, ad_group_id, creative_id, status

SELECT
        id_type, id, campaign_id, ad_group_id, creative_id,
        IF(success_min_ts < fail_min_ts, success_min_ts, fail_min_ts) AS min_ts,
        IF(success_max_ts > fail_max_ts, success_max_ts, fail_max_ts) AS max_ts,
        success_send_cnt, success_send_user_cnt, fail_send_cnt, fail_send_user_cnt
FROM (
    SELECT
            nvl(success_log.id_type, fail_log.id_type) AS id_type,
            nvl(success_log.id, fail_log.id) AS id,
            nvl(success_log.campaign_id, fail_log.campaign_id) AS campaign_id,
            nvl(success_log.ad_group_id, fail_log.ad_group_id) AS ad_group_id,
            nvl(success_log.creative_id, fail_log.creative_id) AS creative_id,
            nvl(fail_log.min_ts, unix_timestamp()* 1000) AS fail_min_ts,
            nvl(success_log.min_ts, unix_timestamp()* 1000) AS success_min_ts,
            nvl(fail_log.max_ts, 0L) AS fail_max_ts,
            nvl(success_log.max_ts, 0L) AS success_max_ts,
            nvl(success_log.send_cnt, 0L) AS success_send_cnt,
            nvl(success_log.send_user_cnt, 0L) AS success_send_user_cnt,
            nvl(fail_log.send_cnt, 0L) AS fail_send_cnt,
            nvl(fail_log.send_user_cnt, 0L) AS fail_send_user_cnt
    FROM (
        SELECT *
        FROM send_log_by_status
        WHERE status = true
    ) AS success_log
    FULL OUTER JOIN
    (
        SELECT *
        FROM send_log_by_status
        WHERE status = false
    ) AS fail_log
    ON success_log.id_type = fail_log.id_type
    AND success_log.id = fail_log.id
)

SELECT  id_type, id,
        count(1) AS click_cnt,
        count(distinct(user_id)) AS click_user_cnt
FROM (
    SELECT meta.*, user_id
    FROM (
        SELECT  explode(meta_arr) AS meta, user_id
        FROM (
            SELECT  array(
                        named_struct('id_type', 'campaign_id', 'id', campaign_id),
                        named_struct('id_type', 'ad_group_id', 'id', ad_group_id),
                        named_struct('id_type', 'creative_id', 'id', creative_id)
                    ) AS meta_arr,
                    user_id,
                    row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY _event_id ORDER BY timestamp DESC) AS rank
            FROM click_log
            WHERE created_at_date = '2021-01-29'
        )
        WHERE rank = 1
    )
)
GROUP BY  id_type, id

SELECT    stat.*, meta.name, meta.type, meta.population
FROM (
    SELECT
            nvl(send_log_aggr.id_type, click_log_aggr.id_type) AS id_type,
            nvl(send_log_aggr.id, click_log_aggr.id) AS id,
            campaign_id,
            ad_group_id,
            creative_id,
            min_ts, max_ts,
            success_send_cnt, success_send_user_cnt, fail_send_cnt, fail_send_user_cnt,
            nvl(click_log_aggr.click_cnt, 0) AS click_cnt,
            nvl(click_log_aggr.click_user_cnt, 0) AS click_user_cnt
    FROM send_log_aggr
    FULL OUTER JOIN click_log_aggr
    ON    send_log_aggr.id_type = click_log_aggr.id_type
    AND   send_log_aggr.id = click_log_aggr.id
) AS stat
LEFT OUTER JOIN meta
ON stat.id_type = meta.id_type
AND stat.id = CAST(meta.id AS STRING)

SELECT    stat.*, meta.name, meta.type, meta.population
FROM (
    SELECT
            nvl(send_log_aggr.id_type, click_log_aggr.id_type) AS id_type,
            nvl(send_log_aggr.id, click_log_aggr.id) AS id,
            campaign_id,
            ad_group_id,
            creative_id,
            min_ts, max_ts,
            success_send_cnt, success_send_user_cnt, fail_send_cnt, fail_send_user_cnt,
            nvl(click_log_aggr.click_cnt, 0) AS click_cnt,
            nvl(click_log_aggr.click_user_cnt, 0) AS click_user_cnt
    FROM send_log_aggr
    FULL OUTER JOIN click_log_aggr
    ON    send_log_aggr.id_type = click_log_aggr.id_type
    AND   send_log_aggr.id = click_log_aggr.id
) AS stat
LEFT OUTER JOIN meta
ON stat.id_type = meta.id_type
AND stat.id = CAST(meta.id AS STRING)

SELECT    current.id,
          current.id_type,
          nvl(current.campaign_id, prev.campaign_id) AS campaign_id,
          nvl(current.ad_group_id, prev.ad_group_id) AS ad_group_id,
          nvl(current.creative_id, prev.creative_id) AS creative_id,
          nvl(prev.min_ts, current.min_ts) AS min_ts,
          nvl(current.max_ts, prev.max_ts) AS max_ts,
          (nvl(current.success_send_cnt, 0) + nvl(prev.success_send_cnt, 0)) AS success_send_cnt,
          (nvl(current.success_send_user_cnt, 0) + nvl(prev.success_send_user_cnt, 0)) AS success_send_user_cnt,
          (nvl(current.fail_send_cnt, 0) + nvl(prev.fail_send_cnt, 0)) AS fail_send_cnt,
          (nvl(current.fail_send_user_cnt, 0) + nvl(prev.fail_send_user_cnt, 0)) AS fail_send_user_cnt,
          (nvl(current.click_cnt, 0) + nvl(prev.click_cnt, 0)) AS click_cnt,
          (nvl(current.click_user_cnt, 0) + nvl(prev.click_user_cnt, 0)) AS click_user_cnt,
          current.name, current.type, current.population
FROM      current_stat AS current
LEFT OUTER JOIN  prev_stat AS prev
ON    current.id_type = prev.id_type
AND   current.id = prev.id

SELECT
           id_type, id, campaign_id, ad_group_id, creative_id, min_ts, max_ts,
           success_send_cnt, success_send_user_cnt, fail_send_cnt, fail_send_user_cnt,
           click_cnt, click_user_cnt,
           start_time, end_time, diff_seconds,
           send_fail_rate, click_count_rate,
           hours, minutes, seconds,
           name, type, population
FROM (
        SELECT  *,
                floor(diff_seconds / 3600) AS hours,
                floor((diff_seconds % 3600) / 60) AS minutes,
                floor(diff_seconds % 60) AS seconds
        FROM (
            SELECT *,
                    date_format(from_utc_timestamp(from_unixtime(min_ts / 1000), 'Asia/Seoul'), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss') AS start_time,
                    date_format(from_utc_timestamp(from_unixtime(max_ts / 1000), 'Asia/Seoul'), 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss') AS end_time,
                    ((max_ts - min_ts) / 1000) AS diff_seconds,
                    CAST(FORMAT_NUMBER(nvl(fail_send_cnt / success_send_cnt * 100, 0), '########.##') AS DOUBLE) AS send_fail_rate,
                    CAST(FORMAT_NUMBER(nvl(click_cnt / success_send_cnt * 100, 0), '########.##') AS DOUBLE) AS click_count_rate,
                    CAST(FORMAT_NUMBER(nvl(click_user_cnt / success_send_user_cnt * 100, 0), '########.##') AS DOUBLE) AS click_user_rate
            FROM   merged_stat
        )
)

UNION ALL

SELECT
           id_type, id, campaign_id, ad_group_id, creative_id, min_ts, max_ts,
           success_send_cnt, success_send_user_cnt, fail_send_cnt, fail_send_user_cnt,
           click_cnt, click_user_cnt,
           start_time, end_time, diff_seconds,
           send_fail_rate, click_count_rate,
           hours, minutes, seconds,
           name, type, population
FROM (
        SELECT
                  prev.*
        FROM prev_stat AS prev
        LEFT OUTER JOIN   current_stat AS current
        ON    current.id_type = prev.id_type
        AND   current.id = prev.id
        WHERE current.id is null
)

                  COUNT(1) AS tx_count
          FROM (
                  SELECT
                          business_id,
                          date_trunc('MONTH', transacted_at) AS timestamp,
                          amount,
                          issuer_name
                  FROM    purchases
                  WHERE   business_id IS NOT NULL
                  AND     transacted_at between '2019-01-01' AND '2020-09-05'
          )
          GROUP BY business_id, issuer_name, timestamp
 ) GROUP BY business_id, timestamp

                  CONCAT(
                      meta.campaign_id, meta.ad_group_id, meta.creative_id,
                      '_',
                      meta.business_id, meta.user_id
                  ) AS message_id,
                  CAST(meta.campaign_id AS INT) AS campaign_id,

                  CAST(meta.user_id AS INT) AS user_id,
                  'EXTRACT' AS step,

                  '' AS error_detail

  LEFT OUTER JOIN ad_history
  ON  n.message_id = ad_history.message_id
  WHERE   ad_history.message_id IS NULL

SELECT
       *,
       row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY business_id, order_month, time_bucket ORDER BY total_amount DESC) AS rank
   FROM
       (
       SELECT
           business_id,
           order_month,
           time_bucket,
           name,
           sum(price) as total_amount,
           count(*) as total_count
       FROM
           (SELECT
               *,
               CASE
                   WHEN order_hour = -1 then '전체'
                   WHEN order_hour between 0 and 5 then '새벽'
                   WHEN order_hour between 6 and 10 then '아침'
                   WHEN order_hour between 11 and 13 then '점심'
                   WHEN order_hour between 14 and 16 then '오후'
                   ELSE '저녁'
               END AS time_bucket
           FROM
               (SELECT
                   business_id,
                   name,
                   CAST(price as integer),
                   order_time,
                   date_format(to_timestamp(order_time, "yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss"), "yyyy-MM-dd") as order_date,
                   date_format(to_timestamp(order_time, "yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss"), "yyyy-MM") as order_month,
                   CAST(date_format(to_timestamp(order_time, "yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss"), "HH") as integer) as order_hour
               FROM
                   pos_app_menus

               UNION ALL

               SELECT
                   business_id,
                   name,
                   CAST(price as integer),
                   order_time,
                   date_format(to_timestamp(order_time, "yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss"), "yyyy-MM-dd") as order_date,
                   date_format(to_timestamp(order_time, "yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss"), "yyyy-MM") as order_month,

               FROM

          collect_list(struct(value, date_id, cnt)) AS message_type
  FROM (
      SELECT  user_id, business_id, date_id, message_type AS value, count(1) AS cnt
      FROM    result_log
      GROUP BY user_id, business_id, date_id, message_type
  )
  GROUP BY user_id, business_id

          user_id, business_id,
          collect_list(struct(value, date_id, cnt)) AS campaign_id
  FROM (
      SELECT  user_id, business_id, date_id, campaign_id AS value, count(1) AS cnt
      FROM    result_log
      GROUP BY user_id, business_id, date_id, campaign_id
  )
  GROUP BY user_id, business_id

SELECT
          user_id, business_id,
          collect_list(struct(value, date_id, cnt)) AS ad_group_id
  FROM (
      SELECT
              user_id, business_id, date_id, ad_group_id AS value, count(1) AS cnt
      FROM (
          SELECT  user_id, business_id, date_id, ad_group_id
          FROM    extract_log
          WHERE   campaign_id = 2

          UNION ALL

          SELECT  user_id, business_id, date_id, ad_group_id
          FROM    result_log
          WHERE   campaign_id != 2
      )
      GROUP BY user_id, business_id, date_id, ad_group_id
  )
  GROUP BY user_id, business_id

SELECT
          IF(m.user_id IS NOT NULL, m.user_id, ad_group_id.user_id) AS user_id,
          IF(m.business_id IS NOT NULL, m.business_id, ad_group_id.business_id) AS business_id,
          m.message_type,
          m.campaign_id,
          ad_group_id.ad_group_id
FROM (
        SELECT
                  IF(message_type.user_id IS NOT NULL, message_type.user_id, campaign_id.user_id) AS user_id,
                  IF(message_type.business_id IS NOT NULL, message_type.business_id, campaign_id.business_id) AS business_id,
                  message_type.message_type,
                  campaign_id.campaign_id
        FROM      message_type
        FULL OUTER JOIN campaign_id
        ON    message_type.user_id = campaign_id.user_id
        AND   message_type.business_id = campaign_id.business_id
) AS m
FULL OUTER JOIN ad_group_id
ON    m.user_id = ad_group_id.user_id
AND   m.business_id = ad_group_id.business_id

SELECT    acquirer_name,
          amount,
          authorization_number,
          business_id,
          card_number,
          card_type,
          credential_key,
          encrypted_card_number,
          estimated_fee AS fee,
          estimated_paid_at,
          installment,
          issuer_name,
          masked_card_number,
          merchant_number,
          amount - estimated_fee - estimated_vat_fee AS payment,
          scraping_type,
          status,
          transacted_at,
          NULLIF(estimated_vat_fee, 0) AS vat_fee,
          created_at,
          updated_at,
          created_at_date
FROM      (
    SELECT    a.*,
              estimate_paid_at(
                  a.issuer_name,
                  c.bank_name,
                  a.transacted_at,
                  COALESCE(c.calculated_purchase_period, 1),
                  COALESCE(c.calculated_payment_period, c.payment_period),
                  c.paid_on_weekends
              ) AS estimated_paid_at,
              CASE
                  WHEN card_type = 1 THEN
                      CAST((a.amount * COALESCE(c.calculated_credit_fee_rate, c.credit_fee_rate) / 100) AS integer)
                  ELSE
                      CAST((a.amount * COALESCE(c.calculated_check_fee_rate, c.check_fee_rate_c) / 100) AS integer)
              END AS estimated_fee,
              CASE
                  WHEN b.vat_withheld AND a.transacted_at > '2019-01-01'
                      THEN CAST(a.amount * 4 / 110 AS integer)
                  ELSE
                      0
              END AS estimated_vat_fee
    FROM      unique_approvals a, businesses b, card_merchants c
    WHERE     a.business_id = b.id
    AND       a.business_id = c.business_id
    AND       a.issuer_name = c.issuer_name
    AND       a.merchant_number = c.merchant_number
)

SELECT  *,
        weekofyear(transacted_at_week) AS week_of_year
FROM    (
  SELECT  st.business_id,
          date_trunc('week', time) AS transacted_at_week,
          SUM(card_sales_amount) AS amount_sum,
          SUM(IF (hour(time) < 18 AND hour(time) >= 6, card_sales_amount, 0)) as day_time_amount_sum,
          SUM(IF (hour(time) >= 18 OR hour(time) < 6, card_sales_amount, 0)) as night_time_amount_sum,
          SUM(IF (weekday(time) > 4, card_sales_amount, 0)) as weekend_amount_sum,
          SUM(IF (weekday(time) <= 4, card_sales_amount, 0)) as weekday_amount_sum,
          SUM(card_sales_amount - returning_amount) as new_amount_sum,
          SUM(returning_amount) as revisit_amount_sum,
          SUM(card_sales_count) as tx_count,
          MAX(st.place.lot_address_1_depth) as lot_address_1_depth,
          MAX(st.place.lot_address_2_depth) as lot_address_2_depth,
          MAX(st.place.lot_address_3_depth) as lot_address_3_depth,
          MAX(st.place.kcd_classification_1_depth) as kcd_classification_1_depth,
          MAX(st.place.kcd_classification_2_depth) as kcd_classification_2_depth,
          MAX(st.place.kcd_classification_3_depth) as kcd_classification_3_depth
  FROM    transactions_stat_with_meta st, targets t
  WHERE   st.business_id = t.business_id
  AND     t.transacted_at_month_count = 13
  AND     st.time_unit = 'day_hour'
  AND     weekofyear(st.time) < weekofyear(current_date())
  GROUP BY 1, 2
)

SELECT      custom_set_id, status,
              users.id AS user_id
  FROM (
    SELECT    custom_set_id, custom_set_value, status
    FROM      custom_set_values
    WHERE     dimension = 'phone_number'
    AND       status in ('RUNNING', 'COMPLETE')
  ) AS custom_set
  JOIN users
  ON custom_set.custom_set_value = users.phone_number

SELECT
          status, user_id,
          collect_set(custom_set_id) AS custom_set_ids
  FROM (
          SELECT  custom_set_id, status, user_id
          FROM    dim_phone_number
  )
  GROUP BY status, user_id

SELECT
          status, user_id,
          collect_set(custom_set_id) AS custom_set_ids
  FROM (
          SELECT  custom_set_id, status, user_id
          FROM    dim_phone_number
  )
  GROUP BY status, user_id

SELECT
          user_id,
          flatten(collect_list(custom_set_ids)) AS custom_set_ids
  FROM    grouped
  GROUP BY user_id

SELECT
      set_new.user_id,
      array_except(
          array_union(
              set_new.custom_set_ids,
              nvl(set_old.custom_set_ids, array(null))
          ),
          array(null)
       ) AS custom_set_ids
FROM (
        SELECT    *
        FROM      grouped
        WHERE     status = 'RUNNING'
) AS set_new
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
        SELECT    *
        FROM      grouped
        WHERE     status = 'COMPLETE'
) AS set_old
ON    set_new.user_id = set_old.user_id

SELECT  /*+ BROADCAST(t) */
        src.*,
        location.sido AS sido,
        location.sigungu AS sigungu,
        location.dong AS dong,
        CASE
          WHEN classification.depth_1_name = '금융/보헙업' THEN '금융/보험업'
          ELSE classification.depth_1_name
        END AS classification_kcd_depth_1_name,
        CASE
          WHEN classification.depth_2_name = '금융/보헙업' THEN '금융/보험업'
          ELSE classification.depth_2_name
        END AS classification_kcd_depth_2_name
FROM    tx_with_meta_src src, (
  SELECT  *
  FROM    targets_src
  WHERE   transacted_at_month_count = 13
) t
WHERE   src.business_id = t.business_id
AND     classification.depth_1_name is not null
AND    (
   (
     time_unit = 'week' AND
     year(time) in (2019, 2020) AND
     weekofyear(time) < weekofyear(current_date()) AND
     weekofyear(time) >= weekofyear(current_date()) - 8
   ) OR
   (
     time_unit = 'day' AND
     time < current_date() AND
     time >= DATE_SUB(current_date(), 7)
   ) OR
   (
     time_unit = 'week' AND
     time >= to_date('2020-01-01', 'yyyy-MM-dd') AND time <= to_date('2020-07-12')
   ) OR

SELECT  /*+ BROADCAST(r, c) */
        CAST(r.id AS bigint) AS region_id,
        CAST(c.id AS bigint) AS classification_id,
        a.sido,
        a.sigungu,
        a.classification_kcd_depth_1_name,
        a.classification_kcd_depth_2_name,
        a.time AS base_date,
        a.time_unit AS date_unit,
        a.business_count,
        a.card_sales_amount,
        a.card_sales_count,
        a.delivery_sales_amount,
        a.delivery_count,
        current_timestamp() AS created_at,
        current_timestamp() AS updated_at
FROM    (
  SELECT  *
  FROM    regions_stat

  UNION ALL

  SELECT  *
  FROM    classifications_stat

  UNION ALL

  SELECT  *
  FROM    multi_dimensions_stat

  UNION ALL

  SELECT  *
  FROM    total_stat
) a LEFT OUTER JOIN regions r
ON (
  a.sido = r.sido AND
  COALESCE(a.sigungu, 'null') = COALESCE(r.sigungu, 'null')
) LEFT OUTER JOIN classification_tree c
ON (
  a.classification_kcd_depth_1_name = c.classification_kcd_depth_1_name AND
  COALESCE(a.classification_kcd_depth_2_name, 'null') = COALESCE(c.classification_kcd_depth_2_name, 'null')
)

SELECT
  _event_id,
  `type`,
  amount,
  authorization_number,
  bill_key,
  bill_no,
  business_id,
  card_number,
  client_id,
  index,
  issuer_name,
  label_name,
  merchant_number,
  order_status,
  paid_at,
  payment_key,
  pos_no,
  pos_type,
  service_name,
  shop_code,
  store_key,
  timestamp,
  CAST(null AS int) AS visit_order,
  created_at_date,
  CAST(unix_timestamp(paid_at, "yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS") AS timestamp) AS transacted_at,
  CAST(to_date(CAST(unix_timestamp(paid_at, "yyyy-MM-dd") AS timestamp), 'yyyy-MM-dd') as string) AS transacted_at_date
FROM    (
  SELECT
    *,
    row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY payment_key ORDER BY timestamp DESC) AS rank
  FROM
    pos_payments_raw
  WHERE
    created_at_date >= '2019-09-23' AND created_at_date < '2020-09-23'
)
WHERE rank = 1

SELECT  business_id,
        card_id,
        status,
        approved_at,
        authorization_number,
        amount,
        MAX(card_name) AS card_name,
        MAX(card_number) AS card_number,
        MAX(created_at) AS created_at,
        MAX(currency) AS currency,
        MAX(installment) AS installment,
        MAX(issuer_name) AS issuer_name,
        MAX(updated_at) AS updated_at,
        MAX(vat) AS vat,
        MAX(vendor_business_name) AS vendor_business_name,
        MAX(vendor_registration_number) AS vendor_registration_number,
        MAX(created_at_date) AS created_at_date
FROM    (
  SELECT    CAST(amount AS int) AS amount,
            to_timestamp(approved_at, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS') AS approved_at,
            authorization_number,
            CAST(business_id AS int) AS business_id,
            CAST(card_id AS int) AS card_id,
            card_name,
            card_number,
            to_timestamp(created_at, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS') AS created_at,
            CAST(currency AS int) AS currency,
            CAST(installment AS int) AS installment,
            issuer_name,
            status,
            to_timestamp(updated_at, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS') AS updated_at,
            vat,
            vendor_business_name,
            vendor_registration_number,
            date_format(to_timestamp(created_at, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS'), 'yyyy-MM-dd') AS created_at_date
  FROM      card_purchases_approvals_src
)
WHERE    created_at_date >= '2021-01-21'
AND      created_at_date < '2021-01-28'
GROUP BY business_id, card_id, status, approved_at, authorization_number, amount

   SELECT *,
          CAST(approved_at AS long) - CAST(lag(approved_at, 1) over (
              PARTITION BY business_id, authorization_number, status, amount
              ORDER BY approved_at
          ) AS long) as buffer
   FROM   card_purchases_approvals
   WHERE  currency = 0
   AND    amount IS NOT NULL
)

  prev.approved_at = current.approved_at AND

  prev.amount = current.amount
)

SELECT
        dim,
        matched_cnt,
        (all_cnt - matched_cnt) AS unmatched_cnt,
        (matched_cnt / all_cnt * 100) AS matched_ratio
FROM (
    SELECT
            *,
            (SELECT count(distinct(business_id)) AS all_business_cnt FROM formatted_old_report_logs) AS all_cnt
    FROM (
        SELECT
                dim,
                count(distinct(business_id)) AS matched_cnt
        FROM (
            SELECT
                    business_id, user_id,
                    matched._1 AS dim,
                    matched._2 AS val
            FROM (
                SELECT
                        o.business_id, o.user_id,
                        explode(compareTowRowWithLongValue(o.data, n.data)) AS matched
                FROM formatted_old_report_logs AS o
                LEFT OUTER JOIN formatted_new_report_logs AS n
                ON o.business_id = n.business_id
            )
        )
        WHERE val = true
        GROUP BY dim
    )
)

SELECT *
FROM
(
    SELECT  '통합' as type,
            '전체' as condition,
            standard_period,
            target_date,
            sum(target_amount) as target_amount_sum,
            sum(standard_amount) as standard_amount_sum,
            sum(target_amount) / (sum(standard_amount) / 7) as rate,
            count(distinct target_businesses_daily_ratio.business_id) as business_count
    FROM    target_businesses_daily_ratio
    GROUP BY 1, 2, 3, 4

    UNION ALL

    SELECT  '지역' as type,
            sido as condition,
            standard_period,
            target_date,
            sum(target_amount) as target_amount_sum,
            sum(standard_amount) as standard_amount_sum,
            sum(target_amount) / (sum(standard_amount) / 7) as rate,
            count(distinct target_businesses_daily_ratio.business_id) as business_count
    FROM    target_businesses_daily_ratio
    WHERE   sido is not null
    GROUP BY 1, 2, 3, 4

    UNION ALL

    SELECT  '업종' as type,
            semas_classification as condition,
            standard_period,
            target_date,
            sum(target_amount) as target_amount_sum,
            sum(standard_amount) as standard_amount_sum,
            sum(target_amount) / (sum(standard_amount) / 7) as rate,
            count(distinct target_businesses_daily_ratio.business_id) as business_count
    FROM    target_businesses_daily_ratio
    WHERE   depth_1_name is not null
    AND     depth_1_name not in ('부동산', '금융,보험', '사회,공공기관', '언론,미디어')
    GROUP BY 1, 2, 3, 4

    UNION ALL

    SELECT  '지역 X 업종' as type,
            concat_ws('>', sido, semas_classification) as condition,
            standard_period,
            target_date,
            sum(target_amount) as target_amount_sum,
            sum(standard_amount) as standard_amount_sum,
            sum(target_amount) / (sum(standard_amount) / 7) as rate,
            count(distinct target_businesses_daily_ratio.business_id) as business_count
    FROM    target_businesses_daily_ratio
    WHERE   sido is not null and depth_1_name is not null
    AND     depth_1_name not in ('부동산', '금융,보험', '사회,공공기관', '언론,미디어')
    GROUP BY 1, 2, 3, 4

    UNION ALL

    SELECT  '업종상세' as type,
            concat_ws('>', depth_1_name, depth_2_name) as condition,
            standard_period,
            target_date,
            sum(target_amount) as target_amount_sum,
            sum(standard_amount) as standard_amount_sum,
            sum(target_amount) / (sum(standard_amount) / 7) as rate,
            count(distinct target_businesses_daily_ratio.business_id) as business_count
    FROM    target_businesses_daily_ratio
    WHERE   depth_1_name is not null and depth_2_name is not null
    AND     depth_1_name not in ('부동산', '금융,보험', '사회,공공기관', '언론,미디어')
    GROUP BY 1, 2, 3, 4
)

       ) AS custom_set_ids

SELECT
   business_id, month, type, address, classification,
   SUM(a_visitors_count) AS a_visitors_count,
   SUM(b_visitors_count) AS b_visitors_count
FROM (
   SELECT
           business_id, month, type, address, classification,
           IF (tag = 'A', visitors_count, 0) AS a_visitors_count,
           IF (tag = 'B', visitors_count, 0) AS b_visitors_count
   FROM (
           SELECT  business_id, min(month) AS month, type, tag, address, classification,
                   approx_count_distinct(encrypted_card_number) AS visitors_count
           FROM    user_tags
           WHERE   type != 'month'
           GROUP BY business_id, type, tag, address, classification

           UNION ALL

           SELECT  business_id, month, type, tag, address, classification,
                   approx_count_distinct(encrypted_card_number) AS visitors_count
           FROM    user_tags
           WHERE   type = 'month'
           GROUP BY business_id, month, type, tag, address, classification
   )
)
GROUP BY business_id, month, type, address, classification

SELECT
   business_id, month, type, address, classification,
   stack(4,
       'A', a_visitors_count,
       'B', b_visitors_count,
       'C', c_visitors_count,
       'C_AVG', CAST(c_visitors_avg AS LONG)
   ) AS (tag, visitors_count)
FROM (
   SELECT
           aggr_user_tags.*,
           (stat.user_cnt - (a_visitors_count + b_visitors_count)) AS c_visitors_count,
           (
               (stat.user_cnt - (a_visitors_count + b_visitors_count)) / (stat.business_cnt - 1)
           ) AS c_visitors_avg
   FROM    aggr_user_tags
   JOIN    stat
   ON      aggr_user_tags.type = stat.type
   AND     aggr_user_tags.month = stat.month
   AND     aggr_user_tags.address = stat.address
   AND     aggr_user_tags.classification = stat.classification
)

SELECT  business_id,
        date,
        sum(IF (type = 'approvals', amount, 0)) as approvals_amount,
        sum(IF (type = 'approvals', payment, 0)) as approvals_payment,
        sum(IF (type = 'approvals', count, 0)) as approvals_count,
        sum(IF (type = 'purchases', payment, 0)) as purchases_payment,
        sum(IF (type = 'purchases', count, 0)) as purchases_count,
        sum(IF (type = 'payments', payment, 0)) as payments_payment,
        sum(IF (type = 'payments', count, 0)) as payments_count
FROM (
      SELECT  business_id,
              'approvals' as type,
              date_trunc('day', transacted_at) as date,
              sum(amount) as amount,
              sum(payment) as payment,
              count(1) as count
      FROM    transactions_without_canceled
      GROUP BY 1, 2, 3

      UNION ALL

      SELECT  business_id,
              'purchases' as type,
              date_trunc('day', purchased_at) as date,
              sum(amount) as amount,
              sum(payment) as payment,
              count(1) as count
      FROM    transactions_without_canceled
      GROUP BY 1, 2, 3

      UNION ALL

      SELECT  business_id,
              'payments' as type,
              date_trunc('day', paid_at) as date,
              sum(amount) as amount,
              sum(payment) as payment,
              count(1) as count
      FROM    transactions_without_canceled
      GROUP BY 1, 2, 3
)
WHERE date is not null
GROUP BY 1, 2

SELECT
       *,
       CASE
           WHEN order_hour = -1 then '전체'
           WHEN order_hour between 0 and 5 then '새벽'
           WHEN order_hour between 6 and 10 then '아침'
           WHEN order_hour between 11 and 13 then '점심'
           WHEN order_hour between 14 and 16 then '오후'
           ELSE '저녁'
       END AS time_bucket
   FROM
       (SELECT
           uid,
           uid_type,
           name,
           price,
           order_time,
           order_month,
           count,
           CAST(date_format(to_timestamp(order_time, "yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss"), "HH") as integer) as order_hour
       FROM
           pos_menus_v2

       UNION ALL

       SELECT
           uid,
           uid_type,
           name,
           price,
           order_time,
           order_month,
           count,
           -1 as order_hour
       FROM
           pos_menus_v2
       )

SELECT
       *,
       row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY uid, uid_type, order_month, time_bucket ORDER BY total_amount DESC) AS rank
   FROM
      (
       SELECT
           uid,
           uid_type,
           order_month,
           time_bucket,
           name,
           sum(price * count) as total_amount,
           sum(`count`) as total_count
       FROM
           pos_menus_with_time_bucket_v2
       GROUP BY
           uid,
           uid_type,
           order_month,
           time_bucket,
           name
      )

SELECT
       *,
       row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY uid, uid_type, order_month, time_bucket ORDER BY total_amount DESC) AS rank
   FROM

       SELECT

           uid_type,
           order_month,
           time_bucket,
           name,
           sum(price * count) as total_amount,
           sum(`count`) as total_count
       FROM
           pos_menus_with_time_bucket_v2
       GROUP BY
           uid,
           uid_type,
           order_month,
           time_bucket,
           name
      )

SELECT

SELECT    *,
          date_trunc('month', date) AS month
FROM      (
  SELECT    business_id,
            time AS date,
            SUM(IF (hour >= 0 AND hour < 6, amount, 0)) AS 0_6_sales_amount,
            SUM(IF (hour >= 6 AND hour < 11, amount, 0)) AS 6_11_sales_amount,
            SUM(IF (hour >= 11 AND hour < 14, amount, 0)) AS 11_14_sales_amount,
            SUM(IF (hour >= 14 AND hour < 17, amount, 0)) AS 14_17_sales_amount,
            SUM(IF (hour >= 17 AND hour < 24, amount, 0)) AS 17_24_sales_amount
  FROM      (
    SELECT    business_id,
              date_trunc('day', time) AS time,
              hour(time) AS hour,
              card_sales_amount AS amount
    FROM      transactions_stat
    WHERE     time_unit = 'day_hour'

    UNION ALL

    SELECT    business_id,
              date_trunc('day', time) AS time,
              hour(time) AS hour,
              (baemin_online_amount_sum + yogiyo_online_amount_sum + baedaltong_online_amount_sum) AS amount

        stats.registration_number,

        stats.status_code,

        CAST(3_month_avg_card_sales_amount AS bigint) AS TR0102_M03,
        3_month_sum_returning_count AS TR0251_M03,
        CAST((1 - 3_month_sum_returning_count / 3_month_sum_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS TR0260_M03,
        CAST((3_month_sum_returning_count / 3_month_sum_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS TR0261_M03,
        6_month_sum_returning_count AS TR0251_M06,
        CAST((1 - 6_month_sum_returning_count / 6_month_sum_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS TR0260_M06,
        CAST(12_month_avg_returning_count AS int) AS TR0256_M12,
        CAST((3_month_sum_card_sales_amount / 6_month_sum_card_sales_amount) * 100 AS int) AS TR4101_M03,
        CAST((3_month_avg_card_sales_amount / 6_month_avg_card_sales_amount) * 100 AS int) AS TR4102_M03,
        CAST((3_month_sum_card_sales_count / 6_month_sum_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS TR4201_M03,
        CAST((3_month_avg_card_sales_count / 6_month_avg_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS TR4202_M03,
        CAST((6_month_sum_card_sales_amount / before_6_month_sum_card_sales_amount) * 100 AS int) AS TR6101_M06,
        CAST((6_month_avg_card_sales_amount / before_6_month_avg_card_sales_amount) * 100 AS int) AS TR6102_M06,
        CAST((6_month_sum_card_sales_count / before_6_month_sum_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS TR6201_M06,
        CAST((6_month_avg_card_sales_count / before_6_month_avg_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS TR6202_M06,
        CAST((3_month_avg_card_sales_amount / last_year_3_month_avg_card_sales_amount) * 100 AS int) AS TR7102_M03,
        CAST((6_month_avg_card_sales_count / last_year_6_month_avg_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS TR7202_M06,
        CAST((3_month_sum_card_sales_count / address_3_month_avg_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS LT8201_M03,
        CAST((6_month_sum_card_sales_amount / classification_6_month_avg_card_sales_amount) * 100 AS int) AS CL8101_M06,
        CAST((6_month_sum_card_sales_count / classification_6_month_avg_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS CL8201_M06,
        CAST((3_month_avg_hometax_sales_amount / 12_month_avg_hometax_sales_amount) * 100 AS int) AS SL5102_M03

LEFT OUTER JOIN address_monthly_stats ON stats.address = address_monthly_stats.address

            concat(concat_ws('-', year, month, day), ' ', hour, ':00:00.000')

SELECT

  bill_key,
  bill_no,
  uid,
  uid_type,
  card_number,
  client_id,
  idx,
  issuer_name,
  label_name,
  merchant_number,
  order_status,
  paid_at,
  payment_key,
  pos_no,
  pos_type,
  service_name,
  shop_code,
  timestamp,

  CAST(created_at_date as string) AS created_at_date,
  paid_at_timestamp AS transacted_at,
  CAST(to_date(paid_at_timestamp, 'yyyy-MM-dd') AS string) AS transacted_at_date
FROM    (
  SELECT
    *,
    COALESCE(
      to_timestamp(paid_at, "yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss"),
      to_timestamp(paid_at, "yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ss"),
      to_timestamp(paid_at, "yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS")
    ) AS paid_at_timestamp,
    row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY payment_key ORDER BY timestamp DESC) AS rank
  FROM
    pos_payments_raw_v2
  WHERE
    created_at_date >= '2020-07-30' AND created_at_date < '2021-01-29'
)
WHERE rank = 1

SELECT
   p._event_id,
   p.`type`,
   p.amount,
   p.authorization_number,
   p.bill_key,
   p.bill_no,
   p.uid,
   p.uid_type,
   COALESCE(c.masked_card_number, p.card_number) as card_number,
   p.client_id,
   p.idx,
   p.issuer_name,
   p.label_name,
   p.merchant_number,
   p.order_status,
   p.paid_at,
   p.payment_key,
   p.pos_no,
   p.pos_type,
   p.service_name,
   p.shop_code,
   p.timestamp,
   p.visit_order,
   p.created_at_date,
   p.transacted_at,
   p.transacted_at_date
 FROM
   pos_payments_distinct_v2 p
 LEFT OUTER JOIN card_sales_transactions c
   ON c.authorization_number = p.authorization_number
   AND date_trunc('hour', c.transacted_at) = date_trunc('hour', p.transacted_at)
   AND c.business_id = p.uid
   AND p.uid_type = 'business_id'
   AND c.amount = p.amount
   AND c.created_at_date >= '2020-07-30' AND c.created_at_date < '2021-01-29'

SELECT
          place_metric.*,
          to_json(region.geometry) AS geometry
  FROM (
  SELECT
          address.sido, address.sigungu, address.sigungu_code,
          place_classification.depth_1_name AS kcd_classification_1_depth,
          COUNT(distinct(business_id)) AS business_cnt,
          SUM(amount_sum) AS amount_sum,
          cast(AVG(amount_sum) as bigint) AS amount_avg,
          SUM(tx_count) AS payment_cnt_sum,
          cast(AVG(tx_count) as bigint) AS payment_cnt_avg,
          cast(AVG(unit_price) as bigint) AS unit_price
  FROM (
      SELECT  meta.business_id,
              address,
              place_classification,
              amount_sum,
              tx_count,
              (amount_sum / tx_count) AS unit_price
      FROM (
              SELECT  business_id,
                      location.common AS address,
                      classification.place AS place_classification
              FROM business_meta
              WHERE classification.place is not null
              AND  location.common is not null
      ) AS meta
      JOIN card_sales_transactions
      ON meta.business_id = card_sales_transactions.business_id
  )
  GROUP BY address.sido, address.sigungu, address.sigungu_code, place_classification.depth_1_name
  HAVING business_cnt > 10
  ) AS place_metric
  LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM total_region WHERE region_type = 'sigungu') AS region
  ON place_metric.sigungu_code = region.code
  ORDER BY sigungu, business_cnt DESC

SELECT
        registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number,
        source_address.address AS full_address,
        source_address.location AS geo_point,
        region.code AS b_code,
        region.sido,
        region.sido_code,
        region.sigungu,
        region.sigungu_code,
        region.dong,
        region.mapping_codes AS h_codes

FROM (
    SELECT
        registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number,
        get_addr_key(lot_address) AS addr_key,
        lot_address AS address,
        IF(
            latitude > 100,
            CONCAT(longitude, ',', latitude),
            CONCAT(latitude, ',', longitude)
        ) AS location
    FROM  naver
    WHERE lot_address is not null
) AS source_address
JOIN (
    SELECT  *
    FROM total_region
    WHERE region_type = 'b_dong'
) AS region
ON source_address.addr_key = region.full_address

SELECT
        registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number,
        source_address.address AS full_address,
        source_address.location AS geo_point,
        region.code AS b_code,
        region.sido,
        region.sido_code,
        region.sigungu,
        region.sigungu_code,
        region.dong,
        region.mapping_codes AS h_codes

FROM (
    SELECT
        registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number,
        get_addr_key(lot_address) AS addr_key,
        lot_address AS address,
        IF(
              latitude > 100,
              CONCAT(longitude, ',', latitude),
              CONCAT(latitude, ',', longitude)
          ) AS location
    FROM  kakao
    WHERE lot_address is not null
) AS source_address
JOIN (
    SELECT  *
    FROM total_region
    WHERE region_type = 'b_dong'
) AS region
ON source_address.addr_key = region.full_address

SELECT
        registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number,
        CAST(null as STRING) AS geo_point,
        source_address.address AS full_address,

        region.sido,
        region.sido_code,

                get_addr_key_sigungu(merchant_address) AS addr_key,

        FROM  merchant_info

) AS region
ON source_address.addr_key = region.full_address

SELECT
          business_id,
          IF (template_type = 'poll' AND answer IS NOT NULL AND answer != '[]', t.id, null) AS complete_poll,
          IF (template_type = 'poll', t.id, null) AS enter_poll,
          IF (template_type = 'application', t.id, null) AS complete_application
  FROM (
      SELECT IF(step_layout = true, 'poll', 'application') AS template_type,
              user_type, id, title
      FROM templates
      WHERE user_type = 'cashnote'
  ) AS t
  JOIN answers
  ON t.id = answers.acceptanced_business_template_id

SELECT
          business_id,
          collect_set(complete_poll) AS complete_polls,
          collect_set(enter_poll) AS enter_polls,
          collect_set(complete_application) AS complete_applications
FROM      template_with_answers
GROUP BY  business_id

SELECT  encrypted_card_number,
        collect_list(
          struct(
            business_id,
            transacted_at
          )
        ) AS histories
FROM    transactions
WHERE   encrypted_card_number is not null
AND     approval_canceled_at IS NULL AND purchase_canceled_at IS NULL
AND     created_at_date >= '2020-01-25'
AND     created_at_date < '2021-01-23'
AND     transacted_at >= '2020-01-25'
AND     transacted_at < '2021-01-23'
AND     (
          (purchased_at is not null AND purchase_canceled_at is null) OR
          (purchased_at is null AND approval_canceled_at is null)
        )
GROUP BY encrypted_card_number

SELECT  business_id,

        authorization_number,
        MAX(price) AS price,
        MAX(vat) AS vat,
        MAX(service) AS service,
        MAX(amount) AS amount,
        MAX(identification_method) AS identification_method,
        MAX(receipt_type) AS receipt_type,
        MAX(created_at) AS created_at,
        MAX(updated_at) AS updated_at,
        MAX(created_at_date) AS created_at_date
FROM    (
  SELECT  CAST(business_id AS int) AS business_id,
          price,
          vat,
          CAST(service AS int) AS service,
          amount,
          authorization_number,
          identification_method,
          CAST(receipt_type AS int) AS receipt_type,
          to_timestamp(sold_at, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS') AS sold_at,
          to_timestamp(created_at, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS') AS created_at,
          to_timestamp(updated_at, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS') AS updated_at,
          date_format(to_timestamp(created_at, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS'), 'yyyy-MM-dd') AS created_at_date
  FROM    hometax_sales_cash_receipts_src
)
WHERE   created_at_date >= '2021-01-21'
AND     created_at_date < '2021-01-28'
GROUP BY  business_id, sold_at, authorization_number

SELECT  business_id,
        purchased_at,
        authorization_number,
        MAX(price) AS price,
        MAX(vat) AS vat,
        MAX(service) AS service,
        MAX(amount) AS amount,
        MAX(tax_deductible) AS tax_deductible,
        MAX(vendor_registration_number) AS vendor_registration_number,
        MAX(vendor_business_name) AS vendor_business_name,
        MAX(vendor_business_code) AS vendor_business_code,
        MAX(identification_method) AS identification_method,
        MAX(receipt_type) AS receipt_type,
        MAX(created_at) AS created_at,
        MAX(updated_at) AS updated_at,
        MAX(vendor_address) AS vendor_address
FROM    (
  SELECT  CAST(business_id AS int) AS business_id,
          to_timestamp(purchased_at, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS') AS purchased_at,
          authorization_number,
          price,
          vat,
          service,
          amount,
          tax_deductible,
          vendor_registration_number,
          vendor_business_name,
          vendor_business_code,
          identification_method,
          CAST(receipt_type AS int) receipt_type,
          to_timestamp(created_at, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS') AS created_at,
          to_timestamp(updated_at, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS') AS updated_at,
          CAST(null AS string) AS vendor_address,
          date_format(to_timestamp(created_at, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS'), 'yyyy-MM-dd') AS created_at_date
