SELECT    *
FROM (
        SELECT
                  nvl(snowdon.registration_number, goose.registration_number) AS registration_number,
                  nvl(snowdon.merchant_number, goose.merchant_number) AS merchant_number,
                  'shinhan' AS card_issuer,
                  nvl(snowdon.classification_code, goose.classification_code) AS classification_code,
                  nvl(snowdon.classification_name, goose.classification_name) AS classification_name
        FROM (
                SELECT
                          card_classification.registration_number,
                          card_classification.card_issuer,
                          card_classification.merchant_number,
                          card_classification.classification_code,
                          shinhancard_classification.classification_name
                FROM  (
                          SELECT  *
                          FROM    merchant_info
                          WHERE   card_issuer = 'shinhan'
                ) card_classification
                LEFT OUTER JOIN   shinhancard_classification
                ON    card_classification.classification_code = shinhancard_classification.classification_code
        ) goose
        FULL OUTER JOIN (
          SELECT  *
          FROM (
                SELECT    registration_number, merchant_number,
                          classification_code, classification_name,
                          row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY registration_number, merchant_number ORDER BY updated_at DESC) AS rank
                FROM      shinhancard_businesses
          )
          WHERE rank = 1
        ) snowdon
        ON    goose.registration_number = snowdon.registration_number
        AND   goose.merchant_number = snowdon.merchant_number
)
WHERE     classification_code IS NOT NULL

  FROM (

          SUM(IF (type = 'hometax_sales_card_transactions', amount, 0)) AS hometax_sales_card_transactions_amount,
          SUM(IF (type = 'hometax_purchases_invoices', amount, 0)) AS hometax_purchases_invoices_amount,

FROM      (
  SELECT  * FROM hometax_sales_stat
  UNION ALL
  SELECT  * FROM hometax_purchases_stat
)
GROUP BY  1, 2, 3

          time,
          time_unit,

          SUM(IF (type = 'hometax_sales_cash_receipts', amount, 0)) AS hometax_sales_cash_receipts_amount,

          SUM(IF (type = 'hometax_purchases_invoices', amount, 0)) AS hometax_purchases_invoices_amount,
          SUM(IF (type = 'hometax_purchases_cash_receipts', amount, 0)) AS hometax_purchases_cash_receipts_amount,

  UNION ALL

              hometax_purchases_cash_receipts_amount
  FROM      hometax_stat
  WHERE     time_unit = 'month'

    time >= '2020-11-19' AND
    time < '2020-11-20'

)

SELECT
        *,
        CONCAT(
                    trim(depth_1_name),'-',
                    trim(depth_2_name), '-',
                    trim(depth_3_name)
        ) AS full_category
FROM (
    SELECT    distinct *
    FROM (
            SELECT  `가맹점(광역시도)` AS sido,
                    `가맹점(시군구)` AS sigungu,
                    `가맹점(행정동)` AS h_dong,
                    `가맹점(PNU)` AS pnu,
                    `업종코드` AS classification_code,
                    `업종대` AS depth_1_name,
                    `업종중` AS depth_2_name,
                    `업종소` AS depth_3_name,
                    `사업자번호` AS registration_number,
                    `가맹점명` AS business_name
            FROM      business_classifications
    )
)

SELECT
          grouped.registration_number,
          grouped.business_name,
          grouped.full_category,
          grouped.merchant_size,
          c.bc_depth_1_code AS depth_1_code,
          c.bc_depth_1_name AS depth_1_name,
          c.bc_depth_2_code AS depth_2_code,
          c.bc_depth_2_name AS depth_2_name,
          c.bc_depth_3_code AS depth_3_code,
          c.bc_depth_3_name AS depth_3_name
FROM  grouped
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
    SELECT    *,
              CONCAT(
                    trim(bc_depth_1_name),'-',
                    trim(bc_depth_2_name), '-',
                    trim(bc_depth_3_name)
              ) AS full_category
    FROM      bccard_classifications
) AS c
ON grouped.full_category = c.full_category

SELECT    valid_info.*,
          merchant_size
FROM (
    SELECT
            SUM(cnt) AS merchant_size,
            filter(collect_list(struct(*)), x -> x.rank == 1)[0] AS valid_info
    FROM (
        SELECT
                registration_number, full_category, cnt, business_names[0] AS business_name,
                rank() OVER (PARTITION BY registration_number ORDER BY cnt DESC) AS rank

        FROM (
            SELECT registration_number, full_category, count(1) AS cnt, collect_set(business_name) AS business_names
            FROM  merged_dedup
            GROUP BY registration_number, full_category
        )
    )
    GROUP BY registration_number
)

SELECT
          grouped.registration_number,
          grouped.business_name,
          grouped.full_category,
          grouped.merchant_size,
          c.bc_depth_1_code AS depth_1_code,
          c.bc_depth_1_name AS depth_1_name,
          c.bc_depth_2_code AS depth_2_code,
          c.bc_depth_2_name AS depth_2_name,
          c.bc_depth_3_code AS depth_3_code,
          c.bc_depth_3_name AS depth_3_name
FROM  grouped
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
    SELECT    *,
              CONCAT(
                    trim(bc_depth_1_name),'-',
                    trim(bc_depth_2_name), '-',
                    trim(bc_depth_3_name)
              ) AS full_category
    FROM      bccard_classifications
) AS c
ON grouped.full_category = c.full_category

SELECT    mappings.business_id,
          depth_1_code, depth_1_name,

SELECT * FROM
     (SELECT
         uid,
         uid_type,
         date_id,
         sum(card_amount) AS total_amount,
         sum(case when card_amount > 0 then 1 else -1 end) AS total_count,
         '카드' as paid_type
     FROM
         (
         SELECT
             *
         FROM
             pos_sales_source_v2
         WHERE
             card_amount != 0
         )
     GROUP BY
         uid,
         uid_type,
         date_id

     UNION ALL

     SELECT
         uid,
         uid_type,
         date_id,
         sum(cash_amount) AS total_amount,
         sum(case when cash_amount > 0 then 1 else -1 end) AS total_count,
         '현금' as paid_type
     FROM
         (
         SELECT
             *
         FROM
             pos_sales_source_v2
         WHERE
             cash_amount != 0
         )
     GROUP BY
         uid,
         uid_type,
         date_id

     UNION ALL

     SELECT
         uid,
         uid_type,
         date_id,
         sum(total_amount) - (sum(cash_amount) + sum(card_amount)) AS total_amount,
         sum(count_src) AS total_count,
         '기타' as paid_type
     FROM
         (
         SELECT
             *,
             CASE WHEN total_amount - (cash_amount + card_amount) > 0 THEN 1 ELSE -1 END AS count_src
         FROM
             pos_sales_source_v2
         WHERE
             total_amount != (cash_amount + card_amount) AND total_amount != 0
         )
     GROUP BY
         uid,
         uid_type,
         date_id
     )

SELECT    struct(approved.*) AS approved,
          struct(canceled.*) AS canceled,
          COALESCE(
            date_format(approved.created_at, 'yyyy-MM-dd'),
            date_format(canceled.created_at, 'yyyy-MM-dd')
          ) AS created_at_date
FROM      (
  SELECT  *
  FROM    current_approvals
  WHERE   status = 0
) approved FULL OUTER JOIN (
  SELECT  *
  FROM    current_approvals
  WHERE   status = 1
) canceled
ON (
  approved.business_id = canceled.business_id AND
  approved.credential_key = canceled.credential_key AND
  approved.amount = -canceled.amount AND
  mask_card_number(approved.card_number) = mask_card_number(canceled.card_number) AND
  approved.authorization_number = canceled.authorization_number AND
  CAST(approved.transacted_at AS DATE) = CAST(canceled.transacted_at AS DATE) AND
  approved.approval_seq = canceled.approval_seq
)

SELECT    approved.*,
          canceled.transacted_at AS approval_canceled_at,
          'cancel' AS type
FROM      approval_candidates
WHERE     approved.business_id is not null AND canceled.business_id is not null

SELECT    p.*,
          c.transacted_at AS approval_canceled_at,
          'late_cancel' AS type
FROM      (
    SELECT    approved.*
    FROM      approval_candidates
    WHERE     canceled.business_id is null
) p, (
    SELECT    canceled.*
    FROM      approval_candidates
    WHERE     approved.business_id is null
) c
WHERE     p.business_id = c.business_id
AND       p.credential_key = c.credential_key
AND       p.amount = -c.amount
AND       p.card_number = c.card_number
AND       p.authorization_number = c.authorization_number

SELECT    /*+ BROADCAST(c) */
          p.approved.*,
          CAST(null AS TIMESTAMP) AS approval_canceled_at,
          'approved' AS type
FROM      approval_candidates p LEFT ANTI JOIN approvals_with_late_cancel c
ON (
  p.approved.business_id = c.business_id AND
  p.approved.credential_key = c.credential_key AND
  abs(p.approved.amount) = abs(c.amount) AND
  p.approved.card_number = c.card_number AND
  p.approved.authorization_number = c.authorization_number AND
  c.approval_canceled_at is not null
)
WHERE     p.canceled.business_id is null

FROM (
  SELECT business_id, tag, collect_list(
                                  struct(
                                       date_format(month, 'yyyy-MM') AS date_month,
                                       visitors_count
                          )) AS monthly_visitor_count
  FROM (
          SELECT    business_id,
                    month,

SELECT
        business_id,
        collect_list(named_struct('user_type', user_type, 'value', sales_amount)) AS visit_user_sales_amount_status,
        collect_list(named_struct('user_type', user_type, 'value', user_count)) AS visit_user_user_count_status,
        collect_list(named_struct('user_type', user_type, 'value', unit_price)) AS visit_user_unit_price_status
FROM (
        SELECT  business_id,
                CASE
                    WHEN visit_count = '1회' THEN 'new'
                    WHEN visit_count = '2회' THEN 'visit_2'
                    WHEN visit_count = '3~9회' THEN 'visit_3_9'
                    WHEN visit_count = '10회이상' THEN 'visit_10_more'
                    ELSE 'etc'
                END AS user_type,
                total_amount AS sales_amount,
                total_card_numbers AS user_count,
                (total_amount / total_transaction_count) AS unit_price
        FROM  snapshot_business_stat
        WHERE type = '12_month'
)
GROUP BY business_id

SELECT
        business_id,
        collect_list(named_struct('user_type', user_type, 'monthly_trend', sales_amount_trend)) AS visit_user_sales_amount_trend,
        collect_list(named_struct('user_type', user_type, 'monthly_trend', user_count_trend)) AS visit_user_user_count_trend,
        collect_list(named_struct('user_type', user_type, 'monthly_trend', unit_price_tend)) AS visit_user_unit_price_trend
FROM (
        SELECT
                business_id,
                user_type,
                collect_list(named_struct('date_month', date_month, 'value', sales_amount)) AS sales_amount_trend,
                collect_list(named_struct('date_month', date_month, 'value', user_count)) AS user_count_trend,
                collect_list(named_struct('date_month', date_month, 'value', unit_price)) AS unit_price_tend
        FROM (
                SELECT  business_id,
                        CASE
                            WHEN visit_count = '1회' THEN 'new'
                            WHEN visit_count = '2회' THEN 'visit_2'
                            WHEN visit_count = '3~9회' THEN 'visit_3_9'
                            WHEN visit_count = '10회이상' THEN 'visit_10_more'
                            ELSE 'etc'
                        END AS user_type,
                        date_format(month, 'yyyy-MM') AS date_month,
                        total_amount AS sales_amount,
                        total_card_numbers AS user_count,
                        (total_amount / total_transaction_count) AS unit_price
                FROM  snapshot_business_stat
                WHERE type = 'month'

        )
        GROUP BY business_id, user_type
)
GROUP BY business_id

SELECT  DISTINCT
        business_id,
        registration_number,
        registration_code,
        status_code
FROM
(
      SELECT  COALESCE(b.business_id, l.business_id) AS business_id,
              COALESCE(b.registration_number, l.registration_number) AS registration_number,
              COALESCE(b.registration_code, '7') AS registration_code,
              CASE
                WHEN b.crefia_registered AND b.hometax_registered THEN '00'
                WHEN b.crefia_registered AND NOT b.hometax_registered THEN '01'
                WHEN NOT b.crefia_registered AND b.hometax_registered THEN '02'
                ELSE '03'
              END AS status_code
      FROM    (
              SELECT  business_id,
                      businesses.businesses.registration_number,
                      IF(businesses.businesses.created_at >= '2020-12-01', '1', '3') AS registration_code,
                      (
                        array_contains(businesses.credentials.types, 'Crefia')
                        OR array_contains(businesses.credentials.types, 'CrefiaBusiness')
                      ) AS crefia_registered,
                      (
                        array_contains(businesses.credentials.types, 'HometaxLogin')
                        OR array_contains(businesses.credentials.types, 'HometaxCertificate')
                      ) AS hometax_registered
              FROM    business_meta
      ) b FULL OUTER JOIN (
              SELECT   business_id,
                       registration_number
              FROM     last_sent_businesses
              WHERE    registration_code != '7'
      ) l ON b.registration_number = l.registration_number
) t
WHERE   t.business_id IS NOT NULL
AND     t.registration_number IS NOT NULL

SELECT
          place_metric.*,
          to_json(region.geometry) AS geometry
  FROM (
  SELECT
          address.sido, address.sigungu, address.sigungu_code,
          place_classification.depth_1_name AS kcd_classification_1_depth,
          COUNT(distinct(business_id)) AS business_cnt,
          SUM(amount_sum) AS amount_sum,
          cast(AVG(amount_sum) as bigint) AS amount_avg,
          SUM(tx_count) AS payment_cnt_sum,
          cast(AVG(tx_count) as bigint) AS payment_cnt_avg,
          cast(AVG(unit_price) as bigint) AS unit_price
  FROM (
      SELECT  meta.business_id,
              address,
              place_classification,
              amount_sum,
              tx_count,
              (amount_sum / tx_count) AS unit_price
      FROM (
              SELECT  business_id,
                      location.common AS address,
                      classification.place AS place_classification
              FROM business_meta
              WHERE classification.place is not null
              AND  location.common is not null
      ) AS meta
      JOIN card_sales_transactions
      ON meta.business_id = card_sales_transactions.business_id
  )
  GROUP BY address.sido, address.sigungu, address.sigungu_code, place_classification.depth_1_name
  HAVING business_cnt > 10
  ) AS place_metric
  LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT * FROM total_region WHERE region_type = 'sigungu') AS region
  ON place_metric.sigungu_code = region.code
  ORDER BY sigungu, business_cnt DESC

SELECT  encrypted_card_number,
          business_id,
          pair._1 as start_date,
          pair._2 as end_date
  FROM    (
          SELECT  encrypted_card_number,
                  business_id,
                  explode(cohort(visits)) as pair
          FROM    (
                  SELECT  encrypted_card_number,
                          business_id,
                          collect_list(transacted_at) as visits
                  FROM    visits
                  WHERE   encrypted_card_number IS NOT NULL
                  AND     business_id IS NOT NULL

                  AND     transacted_at < '2021-01-24'
                  GROUP BY encrypted_card_number, business_id
          )
  )

SELECT

        FROM (
            SELECT  business_id,

        GROUP BY business_id, encrypted_card_number, date

SELECT    business_id,
          time,
          card_sales_amount,
          card_sales_count,
          card_sales_fee,
          card_sales_vat_fee,
          card_sales_payment,
          returning_amount,
          card_sales_amount - returning_amount AS new_amount
FROM (
        SELECT    t.business_id,
                  t.credential_key,
                  date_trunc('month', t.transacted_at) AS time,
                  'month' AS time_unit,
                  COALESCE(SUM(t.amount), 0) AS card_sales_amount,
                  COUNT(*) AS card_sales_count,
                  COALESCE(SUM(t.fee), 0) AS card_sales_fee,
                  COALESCE(SUM(t.vat_fee), 0) AS card_sales_vat_fee,
                  COALESCE(SUM(t.payment), 0) AS card_sales_payment,
                  SUM(IF (t.visit_order > 1, t.amount, 0)) AS returning_amount,
                  SUM(IF (t.visit_order > 1, 1, 0)) AS returning_count
        FROM      transactions t, issuer_purchase_period i
        WHERE     t.business_id = i.business_id
        AND       t.issuer_name = i.issuer_name
        AND       t.merchant_number = i.merchant_number
        AND       (
                      (date_trunc('day', t.transacted_at) > i.limit_date) OR
                      (purchased_at is not null AND purchase_canceled_at is null) OR
                      (approval_canceled_at is not null)
        )
        GROUP BY 1, 2, 3
)

SELECT    *,
          date_trunc('month', date) AS month
FROM      (
  SELECT    business_id,
            time AS date,
            SUM(IF (hour >= 0 AND hour < 6, amount, 0)) AS 0_6_sales_amount,
            SUM(IF (hour >= 6 AND hour < 11, amount, 0)) AS 6_11_sales_amount,
            SUM(IF (hour >= 11 AND hour < 14, amount, 0)) AS 11_14_sales_amount,
            SUM(IF (hour >= 14 AND hour < 17, amount, 0)) AS 14_17_sales_amount,
            SUM(IF (hour >= 17 AND hour < 24, amount, 0)) AS 17_24_sales_amount
  FROM      (
    SELECT    business_id,
              date_trunc('day', time) AS time,
              hour(time) AS hour,
              card_sales_amount AS amount
    FROM      daily_hour_transactions_stat

    UNION ALL

    SELECT    business_id,
              date_trunc('day', time) AS time,
              hour(time) AS hour,
              (baemin_online_amount_sum + yogiyo_online_amount_sum + baedaltong_online_amount_sum) AS amount
    FROM      delivery_app_orders_stat
    WHERE     time_unit = 'day_hour'
  )
  GROUP BY  1, 2
)

              date_trunc('day', time) AS time,
              hour(time) AS hour,
              card_sales_amount AS amount
    FROM      daily_hour_transactions_stat

    UNION ALL

    SELECT    business_id,
              date_trunc('day', time) AS time,
              hour(time) AS hour,
              (baemin_online_amount_sum + yogiyo_online_amount_sum + baedaltong_online_amount_sum) AS amount
    FROM      delivery_app_orders_stat
    WHERE     time_unit = 'day_hour'
  )
  GROUP BY  1, 2
)

          date_trunc('month', date) AS month
FROM      (
  SELECT    business_id,
            time AS date,
            SUM(IF (hour >= 0 AND hour < 6, amount, 0)) AS 0_6_sales_amount,
            SUM(IF (hour >= 6 AND hour < 11, amount, 0)) AS 6_11_sales_amount,
            SUM(IF (hour >= 11 AND hour < 14, amount, 0)) AS 11_14_sales_amount,
            SUM(IF (hour >= 14 AND hour < 17, amount, 0)) AS 14_17_sales_amount,
            SUM(IF (hour >= 17 AND hour < 24, amount, 0)) AS 17_24_sales_amount
  FROM      (
    SELECT    business_id,
              date_trunc('day', time) AS time,
              hour(time) AS hour,
              card_sales_amount AS amount
    FROM      daily_hour_transactions_stat

    UNION ALL

    SELECT    business_id,
              date_trunc('day', time) AS time,
              hour(time) AS hour,
              (baemin_online_amount_sum + yogiyo_online_amount_sum + baedaltong_online_amount_sum) AS amount
    FROM      delivery_app_orders_stat
    WHERE     time_unit = 'day_hour'
  )
  GROUP BY  1, 2
)

        FROM   filtered_business
) AS meta
JOIN paynote_location_mapping
ON array_contains(meta.location_codes, paynote_location_mapping.location_code)

SELECT
        registration_number,
        places.name,

        location.full_address,
        location.b_code,
        location.sigungu_code,
        location.sido_code,

        CONCAT(classification.depth_1_name, '>', classification.depth_2_name, '>', classification.depth_3_name) AS classification_full_name,

        places.reviews.total_review_cnt AS place_review_cnt,
        places.reviews.total_avg_rating AS place_avg_rating,

        cardsales.cashnote.amount_sum AS cashnote_amount_sum,
        cardsales.cashnote.tx_count AS cashnote_tx_count,
        cardsales.paynote_age_band_gender.total_amount_sum AS paynote_amount_sum,
        cardsales.paynote_age_band_gender.total_tx_count AS paynote_tx_count,
        cardsales.paynote_age_band_gender.stats AS age_band_gender_stats,
        cardsales.paynote_age_band.stats AS age_band_stats,
        cardsales.paynote_gender.stats AS gender_stats
FROM   registration_number_meta
WHERE  businesses.merchant_size <= 8
AND    businesses.is_paynote_business = true
AND    classification.depth_1_code = 'D'
AND    classification.depth_2_code != 'D13'

SELECT a.*,
       u.client_user_id,
       u.gender,
       year(current_date()) - year(u.birthday) + 1 AS age,
       u.birthday,
       u.plus_friends
FROM   (
    SELECT p.*,
           m.location.sido,
           m.location.sigungu,
           m.location.dong,
           m.location.geo_point,
           m.classification.depth_1_name,
           m.classification.depth_2_name,
           m.classification.depth_3_name
    FROM   card_payments p LEFT OUTER JOIN registration_number_meta m
    ON     (p.registration_number = m.registration_number)
) a, (
  SELECT  m.client_user_id,
          m.created,
          u.id,
          u.gender,
          u.birthday,
          u.plus_friends
  FROM    users u, client_user_mapping m
  WHERE   u.ci = m.ci
  AND     m.realm_id = 'paynote'
  AND     m.client_id = 'gsshop'
) u
WHERE  a.user_id = u.id

SELECT
            to_timestamp('2021-01-29', 'yyyy-MM-dd') AS timestamp,
            *
  FROM      registration_number_meta
  WHERE     registration_number IS NOT NULL AND registration_number != ''

SELECT meta.*,
       paynote_location_mapping.depth_1_code AS paynote_location_depth_1_code,
       paynote_location_mapping.depth_2_code AS paynote_location_depth_2_code
FROM (
        SELECT
                *,
                array(b_code, sigungu_code, sido_code) AS location_codes
        FROM   filtered_business
) AS meta
JOIN paynote_location_mapping
ON array_contains(meta.location_codes, paynote_location_mapping.location_code)

SELECT
        partition.*,
        registration_number,
        name,
        full_address,
        classification_full_name,
        p_tx_score,
        p_am_score,
        c_tx_score,
        c_am_score
FROM (
        SELECT
                explode(partitions) AS partition, *
        FROM (
                SELECT
                        array(
                            named_struct('type', 'location', 'key', paynote_location_depth_1_code),
                            named_struct('type', 'location', 'key', paynote_location_depth_2_code)
                        ) AS partitions,
                        *,
                        format_number((paynote_tx_count / max_p_tx_score) * 10000, 4) AS p_tx_score,
                        format_number((paynote_amount_sum / max_p_am_score) * 10000, 4) AS p_am_score,
                        format_number((cashnote_tx_count / max_c_tx_score) * 10000, 4) AS c_tx_score,
                        format_number((cashnote_amount_sum / max_c_am_score) * 10000, 4) AS c_am_score
                FROM   filtered_business_with_paynote_location
                CROSS JOIN (
                        SELECT
                                max(paynote_tx_count) AS max_p_tx_score,
                                max(paynote_amount_sum) AS max_p_am_score,
                                max(cashnote_tx_count) AS max_c_tx_score,
                                max(cashnote_amount_sum) AS max_c_am_score
                        FROM   filtered_business_with_paynote_location
                ) AS max_values
                ON 1 = 1
        )
)

SELECT
        partition.*,
        registration_number,
        name,
        full_address,
        classification_full_name,
        p_tx_score,
        p_am_score
FROM (
        SELECT
                explode(partitions) AS partition, *
        FROM (
                SELECT
                        array(
                            named_struct('type', 'location_gender', 'key', CONCAT(paynote_location_depth_1_code, '_', b.key)),
                            named_struct('type', 'location_gender', 'key', CONCAT(paynote_location_depth_2_code, '_', b.key))
                        ) AS partitions,
                        *,
                        format_number((b.values.tx_count / max_p_tx_score) * 10000, 4) AS p_tx_score,
                        format_number((b.values.amount_sum / max_p_am_score) * 10000, 4) AS p_am_score
                FROM  (
                    SELECT
                            stats.*, *
                    FROM (
                        SELECT explode(gender_stats) AS stats, *
                        FROM   filtered_business_with_paynote_location
                    )
                ) AS b
                JOIN (
                    SELECT
                            stats.key,
                            max(stats.values.tx_count) AS max_p_tx_score,
                            max(stats.values.amount_sum) AS max_p_am_score
                    FROM (
                            SELECT explode(gender_stats) AS stats
                            FROM   filtered_business_with_paynote_location
                    )
                    WHERE stats.key is not null
                    GROUP BY stats.key
                ) AS max_values
                ON b.key = max_values.key
        )
)

SELECT
        partition.*,
        registration_number,
        name,
        full_address,
        classification_full_name,
        review_score
FROM (
        SELECT explode(partitions) AS partition, *
        FROM (
                SELECT
                        array(
                              named_struct('type', 'location_review', 'key', paynote_location_depth_1_code),
                              named_struct('type', 'location_review', 'key', paynote_location_depth_2_code)
                        ) AS partitions,
                        *,
                        CAST(
                            format_number((place_review_cnt / max_review_cnt) * 100 * nvl(place_avg_rating, 2.5), 4)
                            AS DOUBLE
                        ) AS review_score
                FROM (
                        SELECT *
                        FROM filtered_business_with_paynote_location
                        WHERE place_review_cnt is not null
                        AND place_review_cnt > 5
                ) AS b
                CROSS JOIN (
                        SELECT
                                max(place_review_cnt) AS max_review_cnt
                        FROM  filtered_business_with_paynote_location
                        WHERE place_review_cnt is not null
                        AND place_review_cnt > 5
                ) AS max_values
                ON 1 = 1
        )
)

SELECT
          registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number,
          arr[0] AS depth_1_name,
          arr[1] AS depth_2_name,
          arr[2] AS depth_3_name,
          arr[3] AS depth_4_name,
          arr[4] AS depth_5_name
FROM (
        SELECT  registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number,
                split(classification, ' > ') AS arr
        FROM    kakao
)

SELECT
        registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number,
        source_address.address AS full_address,
        source_address.location AS geo_point,
        region.code AS b_code,
        region.sido,
        region.sido_code,
        region.sigungu,
        region.sigungu_code,
        region.dong,
        region.mapping_codes AS h_codes

FROM (
    SELECT
        registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number,
        get_addr_key(lot_address) AS addr_key,
        lot_address AS address,
        IF(
              latitude > 100,
              CONCAT(longitude, ',', latitude),
              CONCAT(latitude, ',', longitude)
          ) AS location
    FROM  kakao
    WHERE lot_address is not null
) AS source_address
JOIN (
    SELECT  *
    FROM total_region
    WHERE region_type = 'b_dong'
) AS region
ON source_address.addr_key = region.full_address

SELECT
          registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number,
          arr[0] AS depth_1_name,
          arr[1] AS depth_2_name,
          arr[2] AS depth_3_name,
          arr[3] AS depth_4_name,
          arr[4] AS depth_5_name
FROM (
        SELECT  registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number,
                split(classification, ' > ') AS arr
        FROM    naver
)

SELECT
        registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number,
        source_address.address AS full_address,
        source_address.location AS geo_point,
        region.code AS b_code,
        region.sido,
        region.sido_code,
        region.sigungu,
        region.sigungu_code,
        region.dong,
        region.mapping_codes AS h_codes

FROM (
    SELECT
        registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number,
        get_addr_key(lot_address) AS addr_key,
        lot_address AS address,
        IF(
            latitude > 100,
            CONCAT(longitude, ',', latitude),
            CONCAT(latitude, ',', longitude)
        ) AS location
    FROM  naver
    WHERE lot_address is not null
) AS source_address
JOIN (
    SELECT  *
    FROM total_region
    WHERE region_type = 'b_dong'
) AS region
ON source_address.addr_key = region.full_address

SELECT
      registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number,
      kcd_kakao_mapping.kcd_depth_1_code,
      kcd_kakao_mapping.kcd_depth_2_code,
      kcd_kakao_mapping.kcd_depth_3_code
FROM  kakao_classification
JOIN  kcd_kakao_mapping
ON    kakao_classification.depth_1_name = kcd_kakao_mapping.depth_1_name
AND   kakao_classification.depth_2_name = kcd_kakao_mapping.depth_2_name
AND   nvl(kakao_classification.depth_3_name, 'empty') = nvl(kcd_kakao_mapping.depth_3_name, 'empty')

SELECT
      registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number,
      kcd_naver_mapping.kcd_depth_1_code,
      kcd_naver_mapping.kcd_depth_2_code,
      kcd_naver_mapping.kcd_depth_3_code
FROM  naver_classification
JOIN  kcd_naver_mapping
ON    naver_classification.depth_1_name = kcd_naver_mapping.naver_depth_1_name
AND   naver_classification.depth_2_name = kcd_naver_mapping.naver_depth_2_name

SELECT    struct(purchased.*) AS purchased,
          struct(canceled.*) AS canceled,
          COALESCE(purchased.created_at_date, canceled.created_at_date) AS created_at_date
FROM      (
  SELECT  *
  FROM    current_purchases
  WHERE   amount > 0
) purchased FULL OUTER JOIN (
  SELECT  *
  FROM    current_purchases
  WHERE   amount < 0
) canceled
ON  (
  purchased.business_id = canceled.business_id AND
  purchased.credential_key = canceled.credential_key AND
  purchased.amount = -canceled.amount AND
  purchased.masked_card_number = canceled.masked_card_number AND
  (
      purchased.card_type = 4 AND
      purchased.authorization_number = canceled.authorization_number OR
      (
          purchased.card_type != 4 AND
          CAST(purchased.transacted_at AS DATE) = CAST(canceled.transacted_at AS DATE) AND
          purchased.purchase_cancel_seq = canceled.purchase_cancel_seq
      )
  )
)

SELECT    purchased.*,
          CAST(null AS TIMESTAMP) AS purchase_canceled_at,
          'purchased' AS type
FROM      purchase_candidates
WHERE     canceled.business_id is null

SELECT    purchased.*,
          canceled.purchased_at AS purchase_canceled_at,
          'purchase_cancel' AS type
FROM      purchase_candidates
WHERE     purchased.business_id is not null AND canceled.business_id is not null

SELECT
       *,
       CASE
           WHEN order_hour = -1 then '전체'
           WHEN order_hour between 0 and 5 then '새벽'
           WHEN order_hour between 6 and 10 then '아침'
           WHEN order_hour between 11 and 13 then '점심'
           WHEN order_hour between 14 and 16 then '오후'
           ELSE '저녁'
       END AS time_bucket
   FROM
       (SELECT
           business_id,
           name,
           price,
           order_time,
           order_month,
           count,
           CAST(date_format(to_timestamp(order_time, "yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss"), "HH") as integer) as order_hour
       FROM
           pos_menus

       UNION ALL

       SELECT
           business_id,
           name,
           price,
           order_time,
           order_month,
           count,
           -1 as order_hour
       FROM
           pos_menus
       )

SELECT
       *,
       row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY business_id, order_month, time_bucket ORDER BY total_amount DESC) AS rank
   FROM
      (
       SELECT
           business_id,
           order_month,
           time_bucket,
           name,
           sum(price * count) as total_amount,
           sum(`count`) as total_count
       FROM
           pos_menus_with_time_bucket
       GROUP BY
           business_id,
           order_month,
           time_bucket,
           name
      )

SELECT
       business_id,
       order_month,
       time_bucket,
       sum(total_amount) as total_amount,
       sum(total_count) as total_count,
       to_json(collect_list(struct(rank, name, total_amount, total_count))) as rows
   FROM
       pos_menus_top_k
   GROUP BY
       business_id,
       order_month,
       time_bucket

SELECT

          hourly_sales.`점심` AS `hourly_sales_11_14_amount`,

          hourly_sales.`저녁` AS `hourly_sales_17_24_amount`,

          today_payments.`KB` AS today_payments_kb,

          today_payments.`현대` AS today_payments_hyundai,
          today_payments.`배달의민족` AS today_payments_baemin,
          today_payments.`요기요` AS today_payments_yogiyo,
          today_payments.`배달통` AS today_payments_baedaltong,

          delivery_app_sales.baemin_sales_amount AS delivery_app_sales_baemin_amount,
          delivery_app_sales.yogiyo_sales_amount AS delivery_app_sales_yogiyo_amount,
          delivery_app_sales.baedaltong_sales_amount AS delivery_app_sales_baedaltong_amount,
          delivery_app_sales.monthly_delivery_app_sales AS delivery_app_sales_monthly_amount,

          card_purchases.monthly_card_purchases AS card_purchases_monthly_amount,
          CAST(hometax_sales.monthly_invoice_sales_amount AS LONG) AS hometax_sales_monthly_invoice_amount,
          CAST(hometax_sales.monthly_cash_sales_amount AS LONG) AS hometax_sales_monthly_cash_amount,
          CAST(hometax_purchases.monthly_cash_purchases AS LONG) AS hometax_purchases_monthly_cash_amount,
          CAST(hometax_purchases.monthly_invoice_purchases AS LONG) AS hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount,

          transform(future_payments, m -> named_struct('amount', m.amount, 'date', CONCAT(date_format(m.date, 'd일'), '(', dayofweek_kor(m.date), ')')))
          AS future_payments_arr,
          transform(bank_accounts, m -> named_struct('bank_name', m.bank_name, 'account_number', CONCAT('*', SUBSTRING(m.account_number, -5)), 'balance', nvl(m.balance, 0), 'unused', IF(m.balance IS null, true, false)))
          AS bank_accounts_arr,
          transform(card_purchases.today_purchases, m -> named_struct('amount', nvl(m.amount, 0), 'count', m.count, 'issuer', m.card.issuer, 'number', CONCAT('*', SUBSTRING(m.card.number, -4))   ))
          AS today_card_purchases_arr
FROM (
        SELECT    id, group_id, target_id, business_id, user_id,
                  nvl(payload.title, '') AS title,
                  payload.attachment, payload.template_code,
                  payload.attachment.button[0].url_mobile AS url_mobile,
                  payload.raw_data.*
        FROM (
              SELECT  id, group_id, CONCAT(user_id, '_', business_id) AS target_id,
                      business_id, user_id,
                      from_json(bzm_payload, 'STRUCT<`attachment`: STRUCT<`button`: ARRAY<STRUCT<`name`: STRING, `type`: STRING, `url_mobile`: STRING>>>, `raw_data`: STRUCT<`bank_accounts`: ARRAY<STRUCT<`account_number`: STRING, `balance`: BIGINT, `bank_name`: STRING>>, `card_purchases`: STRUCT<`monthly_card_purchases`: BIGINT, `today_purchases`: ARRAY<STRUCT<`amount`: BIGINT, `card`: STRUCT<`business_id`: BIGINT, `card_type`: STRING, `created_at`: STRING, `credential_id`: BIGINT, `id`: BIGINT, `issuer`: STRING, `name`: STRING, `number`: STRING, `updated_at`: STRING, `uuid`: STRING>, `count`: BIGINT>>>, `card_sales`: STRUCT<`card_sales_amount`: BIGINT, `card_sales_count`: BIGINT, `card_sales_fee`: BIGINT, `card_sales_payment`: BIGINT, `card_sales_vat_fee`: BIGINT, `monthly_card_sales`: BIGINT, `new_amount`: BIGINT, `returning_amount`: BIGINT>, `delivery_app_sales`: STRUCT<`baedaltong_sales_amount`: BIGINT, `baemin_sales_amount`: BIGINT, `monthly_delivery_app_sales`: BIGINT, `yogiyo_sales_amount`: BIGINT>, `future_payments`: ARRAY<STRUCT<`amount`: BIGINT, `date`: STRING>>, `hometax_purchases`: STRUCT<`monthly_cash_purchases`: STRING, `monthly_invoice_purchases`: STRING>, `hometax_sales`: STRUCT<`monthly_cash_sales_amount`: STRING, `monthly_invoice_sales_amount`: STRING>, `hourly_sales`: STRUCT<`미분류`: BIGINT, `새벽`: BIGINT, `아침`: BIGINT, `오후`: BIGINT, `저녁`: BIGINT, `점심`: BIGINT>, `today_payments`: STRUCT<`KB`: BIGINT, `농협NH`: BIGINT, `롯데`: BIGINT, `배달의민족`: BIGINT, `요기요`: BIGINT, `배달통`: BIGINT, `비씨`: BIGINT, `삼성`: BIGINT, `신한`: BIGINT, `하나`: BIGINT, `현대`: BIGINT>>, `template_code`: STRING, `title`: STRING>', map())
                      AS payload
              FROM    report_logs
              WHERE   id > 398030145
              AND     group_id in ('0aedb1b7-7b73-4f94-9361-c49e3480efe3','e365a43e-c321-4f54-a6f5-dbc1245228a6')
              AND     report_type = 'daily'
              AND     business_id IS NOT NULL
              AND     user_id IS NOT NULL
        )
)

                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount'),n.hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount, o.hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount) AS hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount,

SELECT    *,
          date_format('2021-01-28', 'M월') AS report_month,
          date_format('2021-01-28', 'M월 d일') AS report_date,
          dayofweek_kor('2021-01-28') AS report_day_of_week,
          date_format('2021-01-29', 'M월 d일') AS today_date,
          dayofweek_kor('2021-01-29') AS today_day_of_week,

          IF(bank_account_etc_count > 0, true, false) AS bank_account_etc_exists,
          IF(today_card_purchases_etc_count > 0, true, false) AS today_card_purchases_etc_exists,
          IF(size(delivery_app_sales) > 0, true, false) AS delivery_app_sales_exists,
          IF(size(today_payments) > 0, true, false) AS today_payments_exists,
          IF(size(future_payments) > 0, true, false) AS future_payments_exists
FROM (
        SELECT    target_id, business_id, user_id, title, template_code, url_mobile,

                  FORMAT_NUMBER(card_sales_amount, 0) AS card_sales_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(card_sales_count, 0) AS card_sales_count,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(card_sales_fee, 0) AS card_sales_fee,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(card_sales_vat_fee, 0) AS card_sales_vat_fee,
                  IF(card_sales_vat_fee > 0, true, false) AS card_sales_vat_fee_exists,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(card_sales_payment, 0) AS card_sales_payment,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(card_sales_new_amount, 0) AS card_sales_new_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(card_sales_returning_amount, 0) AS card_sales_returning_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(card_sales_monthly_amount, 0) AS card_sales_monthly_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(delivery_app_sales_monthly_amount, 0) AS delivery_app_sales_monthly_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(card_purchases_monthly_amount, 0) AS card_purchases_monthly_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hometax_sales_monthly_invoice_amount, 0) AS hometax_sales_monthly_invoice_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hometax_sales_monthly_cash_amount, 0) AS hometax_sales_monthly_cash_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hometax_purchases_monthly_cash_amount, 0) AS hometax_purchases_monthly_cash_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount, 0) AS hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount,

                  NVL(FORMAT_NUMBER(FLOOR(card_sales_amount / card_sales_count), 0), '0') AS card_sales_unit_price,
                  NVL(FORMAT_NUMBER(ROUND(card_sales_new_amount / card_sales_amount * 100), 0), '0') AS card_sales_new_amount_percent,
                  NVL(FORMAT_NUMBER(ROUND(card_sales_returning_amount / card_sales_amount * 100), 0), '0') AS card_sales_returning_amount_percent,
                  IF(card_sales_amount > 0, true, false) AS card_sales_amount_exists,

                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hourly_sales_0_6_amount, 0) AS hourly_sales_0_6_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hourly_sales_6_11_amount, 0) AS hourly_sales_6_11_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hourly_sales_11_14_amount, 0) AS hourly_sales_11_14_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hourly_sales_14_17_amount, 0) AS hourly_sales_14_17_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hourly_sales_17_24_amount, 0) AS hourly_sales_17_24_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(hourly_sales_etc_amount, 0) AS hourly_sales_etc_amount,
                  NVL(FORMAT_NUMBER(ROUND(hourly_sales_0_6_amount / hourly_sales_amount_sum * 100), 0), '0') AS hourly_sales_0_6_amount_percent,
                  NVL(FORMAT_NUMBER(ROUND(hourly_sales_6_11_amount / hourly_sales_amount_sum * 100), 0), '0') AS hourly_sales_6_11_amount_percent,
                  NVL(FORMAT_NUMBER(ROUND(hourly_sales_11_14_amount / hourly_sales_amount_sum * 100), 0), '0') AS hourly_sales_11_14_amount_percent,
                  NVL(FORMAT_NUMBER(ROUND(hourly_sales_14_17_amount / hourly_sales_amount_sum * 100), 0), '0') AS hourly_sales_14_17_amount_percent,
                  NVL(FORMAT_NUMBER(ROUND(hourly_sales_17_24_amount / hourly_sales_amount_sum * 100), 0), '0') AS hourly_sales_17_24_amount_percent,
                  NVL(FORMAT_NUMBER(ROUND(hourly_sales_etc_amount / hourly_sales_amount_sum * 100), 0), '0') AS hourly_sales_etc_amount_percent,
                  IF(hourly_sales_etc_amount > 0, true, false) AS hourly_sales_etc_amount_exists,
                  IF(hourly_sales_amount_sum > 0, true, false) AS hourly_sales_exists,

                  FORMAT_NUMBER(delivery_app_sales_baemin_amount, 0) AS delivery_app_sales_baemin_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(delivery_app_sales_yogiyo_amount, 0) AS delivery_app_sales_yogiyo_amount,
                  FORMAT_NUMBER(delivery_app_sales_baedaltong_amount, 0) AS delivery_app_sales_baedaltong_amount,

                  filter(today_payments_arr, d -> d.amount > 0) AS today_payments,
                  aggregate(today_payments_arr, 0L, (acc, d) -> acc + d.amount) AS today_payments_sum_amount,

                  future_payments_arr AS future_payments,
                  aggregate(future_payments_arr, 0L, (acc, d) -> acc + d.amount) AS future_payments_sum_amount,

                  slice(bank_accounts_arr, 1, 5) AS bank_accounts,
                  IF(size(bank_accounts_arr) > 5, size(bank_accounts_arr) - 5, 0) AS bank_account_etc_count,

                  slice(today_card_purchases_arr, 1, 5) AS today_card_purchases,
                  IF(size(today_card_purchases_arr) > 5, size(today_card_purchases_arr) - 5, 0) AS today_card_purchases_etc_count,

                  filter(delivery_app_sales_arr, d -> d.amount > 0) AS delivery_app_sales,

                  (
                      card_sales_monthly_amount +
                      delivery_app_sales_monthly_amount +
                      hometax_sales_monthly_invoice_amount +
                      hometax_sales_monthly_cash_amount
                  ) AS monthly_sales_sum,
                  (
                      card_purchases_monthly_amount +
                      hometax_purchases_monthly_cash_amount +
                      hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount
                  ) AS monthly_purchases_sum
        FROM      merged
)

SELECT    *
FROM (
        SELECT    calc_additional_columns.*,
                  b.*,
                  IF(c.confirmed, 'daily_reports', 'daily_reports_wo_crefia') AS report_name
        FROM      calc_additional_columns
        LEFT OUTER JOIN   businesses_info AS b
        ON        calc_additional_columns.business_id = b.id
        LEFT OUTER JOIN   crefia_credential AS c
        ON        calc_additional_columns.business_id = c.business_id
) r
CROSS JOIN outdated_issuers
SELECT CAST(max(id) AS STRING) AS value FROM formatted_report_logs

SELECT    *,
          (hourly_sales_0_6_amount + hourly_sales_6_11_amount + hourly_sales_11_14_amount + hourly_sales_14_17_amount + hourly_sales_17_24_amount + hourly_sales_etc_amount) AS hourly_sales_amount_sum
FROM (
SELECT    target_id, business_id, user_id, title, template_code, url_mobile,
          NVL(card_sales_amount, 0) AS card_sales_amount,
          NVL(card_sales_count, 0) AS card_sales_count,
          NVL(card_sales_fee, 0) AS card_sales_fee,
          NVL(card_sales_vat_fee, 0) AS card_sales_vat_fee,
          NVL(card_sales_payment, 0) AS card_sales_payment,
          NVL(card_sales_new_amount, 0) AS card_sales_new_amount,
          NVL(card_sales_returning_amount, 0) AS card_sales_returning_amount,
          NVL(card_sales_monthly_amount, 0) AS card_sales_monthly_amount,
          NVL(hourly_sales_0_6_amount, 0) AS hourly_sales_0_6_amount,
          NVL(hourly_sales_6_11_amount, 0) AS hourly_sales_6_11_amount,
          NVL(hourly_sales_11_14_amount, 0) AS hourly_sales_11_14_amount,
          NVL(hourly_sales_14_17_amount, 0) AS hourly_sales_14_17_amount,
          NVL(hourly_sales_17_24_amount, 0) AS hourly_sales_17_24_amount,
          NVL(hourly_sales_etc_amount, 0) AS hourly_sales_etc_amount,
          NVL(delivery_app_sales_monthly_amount, 0) AS delivery_app_sales_monthly_amount,
          NVL(card_purchases_monthly_amount, 0) AS card_purchases_monthly_amount,
          NVL(hometax_sales_monthly_invoice_amount, 0) AS hometax_sales_monthly_invoice_amount,
          NVL(hometax_sales_monthly_cash_amount, 0) AS hometax_sales_monthly_cash_amount,
          NVL(hometax_purchases_monthly_cash_amount, 0) AS hometax_purchases_monthly_cash_amount,
          NVL(hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount, 0) AS hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount,
          NVL(delivery_app_sales_baemin_amount, 0) AS delivery_app_sales_baemin_amount,
          NVL(delivery_app_sales_yogiyo_amount, 0) AS delivery_app_sales_yogiyo_amount,
          NVL(delivery_app_sales_baedaltong_amount, 0) AS delivery_app_sales_baedaltong_amount,
          array(
              named_struct('issuer_name', 'KB', 'amount', nvl(today_payments_kb, 0L)),
              named_struct('issuer_name', '농협NH', 'amount', nvl(today_payments_nh, 0L)),
              named_struct('issuer_name', '롯데', 'amount', nvl(today_payments_lotte, 0L)),
              named_struct('issuer_name', '비씨', 'amount', nvl(today_payments_bc, 0L)),
              named_struct('issuer_name', '삼성', 'amount', nvl(today_payments_samsung, 0L)),
              named_struct('issuer_name', '신한', 'amount', nvl(today_payments_shinhan, 0L)),
              named_struct('issuer_name', '하나', 'amount', nvl(today_payments_hana, 0L)),
              named_struct('issuer_name', '현대', 'amount', nvl(today_payments_hyundai, 0L)),
              named_struct('issuer_name', '배달의민족', 'amount', nvl(today_payments_baemin, 0L)),
              named_struct('issuer_name', '요기요', 'amount', nvl(today_payments_yogiyo, 0L)),
              named_struct('issuer_name', '배달통', 'amount', nvl(today_payments_baedaltong, 0L))
          ) AS today_payments_arr,
          array(
              named_struct('app_name', '배달의민족', 'amount', delivery_app_sales_baemin_amount),
              named_struct('app_name', '요기요', 'amount', delivery_app_sales_yogiyo_amount),
              named_struct('app_name', '배달통', 'amount', delivery_app_sales_baedaltong_amount)
          ) AS delivery_app_sales_arr,
          future_payments_arr,
          bank_accounts_arr,
          today_card_purchases_arr
FROM (
        SELECT
                  o.target_id, o.business_id, o.user_id, o.title, o.template_code, o.url_mobile,

                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'card_sales_amount'),           n.card_sales_amount, o.card_sales_amount) AS card_sales_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'card_sales_count'),            n.card_sales_count, o.card_sales_count) AS card_sales_count,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'card_sales_fee'),              n.card_sales_fee, o.card_sales_fee) AS card_sales_fee,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'card_sales_vat_fee'),          n.card_sales_vat_fee, o.card_sales_vat_fee) AS card_sales_vat_fee,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'card_sales_payment'),          n.card_sales_payment, o.card_sales_payment) AS card_sales_payment,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'card_sales_new_amount'),       n.card_sales_new_amount, o.card_sales_new_amount) AS card_sales_new_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'card_sales_returning_amount'), n.card_sales_returning_amount, o.card_sales_returning_amount) AS card_sales_returning_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'card_sales_monthly_amount'),   n.card_sales_monthly_amount, o.card_sales_monthly_amount) AS card_sales_monthly_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'hourly_sales_0_6_amount'),     n.hourly_sales_0_6_amount, o.hourly_sales_0_6_amount) AS hourly_sales_0_6_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'hourly_sales_6_11_amount'),    n.hourly_sales_6_11_amount, o.hourly_sales_6_11_amount) AS hourly_sales_6_11_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'hourly_sales_11_14_amount'),   n.hourly_sales_11_14_amount, o.hourly_sales_11_14_amount) AS hourly_sales_11_14_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'hourly_sales_14_17_amount'),   n.hourly_sales_14_17_amount, o.hourly_sales_14_17_amount) AS hourly_sales_14_17_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'hourly_sales_17_24_amount'),   n.hourly_sales_17_24_amount, o.hourly_sales_17_24_amount) AS hourly_sales_17_24_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_kb'),           n.today_payments_kb, o.today_payments_kb) AS today_payments_kb,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_nh'),           n.today_payments_nh, o.today_payments_nh) AS today_payments_nh,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_lotte'),        n.today_payments_lotte, o.today_payments_lotte) AS today_payments_lotte,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_baemin'),       n.today_payments_baemin, o.today_payments_baemin) AS today_payments_baemin,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_bc'),           n.today_payments_bc, o.today_payments_bc) AS today_payments_bc,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_samsung'),      n.today_payments_samsung, o.today_payments_samsung) AS today_payments_samsung,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_shinhan'),      n.today_payments_shinhan, o.today_payments_shinhan) AS today_payments_shinhan,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_hana'),         n.today_payments_hana, o.today_payments_hana) AS today_payments_hana,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_hyundai'),      n.today_payments_hyundai, o.today_payments_hyundai) AS today_payments_hyundai,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_yogiyo'),       n.today_payments_yogiyo, o.today_payments_yogiyo) AS today_payments_yogiyo,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'today_payments_baedaltong'),   n.today_payments_baedaltong, o.today_payments_baedaltong) AS today_payments_baedaltong,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'delivery_app_sales_baemin_amount'),        n.delivery_app_sales_baemin_amount, o.delivery_app_sales_baemin_amount) AS delivery_app_sales_baemin_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'delivery_app_sales_yogiyo_amount'),        n.delivery_app_sales_yogiyo_amount, o.delivery_app_sales_yogiyo_amount) AS delivery_app_sales_yogiyo_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'delivery_app_sales_baedaltong_amount'),    n.delivery_app_sales_baedaltong_amount, o.delivery_app_sales_baedaltong_amount) AS delivery_app_sales_baedaltong_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'delivery_app_sales_monthly_amount'),       n.delivery_app_sales_monthly_amount, o.delivery_app_sales_monthly_amount) AS delivery_app_sales_monthly_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'card_purchases_monthly_amount'),           n.card_purchases_monthly_amount, o.card_purchases_monthly_amount) AS card_purchases_monthly_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'hometax_sales_monthly_invoice_amount'),    n.hometax_sales_monthly_invoice_amount, o.hometax_sales_monthly_invoice_amount) AS hometax_sales_monthly_invoice_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'hometax_sales_monthly_cash_amount'),       n.hometax_sales_monthly_cash_amount, o.hometax_sales_monthly_cash_amount) AS hometax_sales_monthly_cash_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'hometax_purchases_monthly_cash_amount'),   n.hometax_purchases_monthly_cash_amount, o.hometax_purchases_monthly_cash_amount) AS hometax_purchases_monthly_cash_amount,
                  IF(array_contains(array('card_sales_amount', 'card_sales_count', 'card_sales_fee', 'card_sales_vat_fee'), 'hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount'),n.hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount, o.hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount) AS hometax_purchases_monthly_invoice_amount,
                  o.hourly_sales_etc_amount,
                  o.future_payments_arr,
                  o.bank_accounts_arr,
                  o.today_card_purchases_arr
        FROM      formatted_report_logs AS o
        LEFT OUTER JOIN   formatted_daily_report AS n
        ON        o.business_id = n.business_id
)
)

SELECT  DISTINCT registration_number
  FROM    card_payments
  WHERE   approved_at between '2019-01-01' AND '2021-01-28'

SELECT *
FROM   card_payments_src
WHERE  date_trunc('month', approved_at) >= add_months(date_trunc('month', current_date()), -2)
AND    date_trunc('month', approved_at) < date_trunc('month', current_date())

SELECT    registration_number,
          collect_set(struct(card_issuer, merchant_number)) AS merchants,
          collect_set(card_issuer) AS card_issuers
FROM (
        SELECT
                registration_number, merchant_number,
                CASE
                    WHEN card_issuer = 'bc' THEN '비씨'
                    WHEN card_issuer = 'shinhan' THEN '신한'
                    WHEN card_issuer = 'hyundai' THEN '현대'
                    ELSE card_issuer
                END AS card_issuer
        FROM (
            SELECT DISTINCT registration_number, merchant_number, card_issuer
            FROM  card_payments
            WHERE card_issuer is not null
        )
)
GROUP BY registration_number

SELECT    *
FROM (
        SELECT    DISTINCT registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number,
                  merchant, classification_code, merchant_code_name, merchant_address,
                  row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number ORDER BY updated_at DESC) AS rank
        FROM      card_payments
        WHERE     card_issuer is not null
        AND       registration_number is not null
)
WHERE   rank = 1

SELECT  'card_payments' AS table, max(id) AS latest_id
  FROM    card_payments
  WHERE   created_at > (SELECT max(created_at_date) FROM card_payments)

  UNION ALL

  SELECT  'access_logs' AS table, max(id) AS latest_id
  FROM    access_logs
  WHERE   created_at > (SELECT max(created_at_date) FROM access_logs)

  UNION ALL

  SELECT  'user_events' AS table, max(id) AS latest_id
  FROM    user_events
  WHERE   created_at > (SELECT max(created_at_date) FROM user_events)

SELECT    registration_number, card_issuer, classification_code, merchant_code_name AS classification_name
FROM (
        SELECT    registration_number, card_issuer, classification_code, merchant_code_name,
                  row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY registration_number, card_issuer ORDER BY updated_at DESC) AS rank
        FROM      card_payments
        WHERE     card_issuer is not null
)
WHERE   rank = 1

SELECT
         payment.*,
         paynote_users.gender,
         paynote_users.age_band
 FROM (
     SELECT
             date_trunc('MONTH', approved_at) AS timestamp,
             registration_number,
             user_id,
             amount
     FROM    card_payments
     WHERE   approved_at between '2020-08-01' AND '2021-01-28'
     AND     card_issuer IS NOT NULL
 ) AS payment
 JOIN paynote_users
 ON payment.user_id = paynote_users.user_id

SELECT
          user_id, timestamp,
          registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number,
          SUM(amount) AS amount_sum,
          COUNT(1) AS tx_count
  FROM (
          SELECT
                  user_id,
                  date_trunc('MONTH', approved_at) AS timestamp,
                  registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number,
                  amount
          FROM    card_payments
          WHERE   approved_at between '2019-01-01' AND '2021-01-29'
          AND     card_issuer IS NOT NULL
 )
 GROUP BY user_id, timestamp, registration_number, card_issuer, merchant_number

SELECT
          cashnote_businesses.id AS business_id,
          true AS is_paynote_business
  FROM    cashnote_businesses
  JOIN paynote_businesses
  ON  cashnote_businesses.registration_number = paynote_businesses.registration_number

SELECT
      business_id,
      kcd_naver_mapping.kcd_depth_1_code,
      kcd_naver_mapping.kcd_depth_2_code,
      kcd_naver_mapping.kcd_depth_3_code
FROM  naver_classification
JOIN  kcd_naver_mapping
ON    naver_classification.depth_1_name = kcd_naver_mapping.naver_depth_1_name
AND   naver_classification.depth_2_name = kcd_naver_mapping.naver_depth_2_name

SELECT
      business_id,
      kcd_kakao_mapping.kcd_depth_1_code,
      kcd_kakao_mapping.kcd_depth_2_code,
      kcd_kakao_mapping.kcd_depth_3_code
FROM  kakao_classification
JOIN  kcd_kakao_mapping
ON    kakao_classification.depth_1_name = kcd_kakao_mapping.depth_1_name
AND   kakao_classification.depth_2_name = kcd_kakao_mapping.depth_2_name
AND   nvl(kakao_classification.depth_3_name, 'empty') = nvl(kcd_kakao_mapping.depth_3_name, 'empty')

SELECT
          business_id,
          kcd_depth_1_code,
          kcd_depth_2_code,
          kcd_depth_3_code
  FROM    hometax_classification
  JOIN    hometax_kcd_mapping
  ON  hometax_classification.classification_code = hometax_kcd_mapping.classification_code

SELECT    business_id,
          kcd_depth_1_code,
          kcd_depth_2_code,
          kcd_depth_3_code
FROM  shinhancard_classification
JOIN  shinhancard_kcd_mapping AS mapping
ON    shinhancard_classification.classification_code = mapping.classification_code

SELECT    business_id,
          kcd_depth_1_code,
          kcd_depth_2_code,
          kcd_depth_3_code
FROM  bccard_classification
JOIN  bccard_kcd_mapping AS mapping
ON    bccard_classification.depth_3_code = mapping.classification_code

SELECT    business_id,
          kcd_depth_1_code,
          kcd_depth_2_code,
          kcd_depth_3_code
FROM  hyundaicard_classification
JOIN  hyundaicard_kcd_mapping AS mapping
ON    hyundaicard_classification.classification_code = mapping.classification_code

SELECT
        business_id,
        kcd_depth_1_code,
        kcd_depth_2_code,
        kcd_depth_3_code
FROM (
    SELECT
            c.business_id,
            m.kcd_depth_1_code,
            m.kcd_depth_2_code,
            m.kcd_depth_3_code,
            row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY c.business_id ORDER BY m.kcd_depth_3_code) AS rank
    FROM (
        SELECT business_id, explode(codes) AS code
        FROM franchise_classification
    ) AS c
    JOIN franchise_kcd_mapping AS m
    ON c.code.company_code = m.franchise_company_code
    AND c.code.brand_code = m.franchise_brand_code
)
WHERE rank =1

SELECT
          business_id,
          kcd_depth_1_code,

SELECT

          business_id,
          date_format(timestamp, 'yyyy-MM-dd') AS date_id,
          SUM(amount_sum) AS amount_sum,
          SUM(tx_count) AS tx_count,
          SUM(cancel_count) AS cancel_count,
          SUM(installment_count) AS installment_count,
          map_from_entries(collect_list(struct(issuer_name, amount_sum))) AS issuer_amount_sum,
          map_from_entries(collect_list(struct(issuer_name, tx_count))) AS issuer_tx_count
  FROM (
          SELECT
                  timestamp,
                  business_id,
                  issuer_name,
                  SUM(cancel_count) AS cancel_count,
                  SUM(installment_count) AS installment_count,
                  SUM(amount) AS amount_sum,
                  COUNT(1) AS tx_count
          FROM (
                  SELECT
                          business_id,
                          date_trunc('MONTH', transacted_at) AS timestamp,
                          amount,
                          issuer_name,
                          IF(status = 1, 1, 0) cancel_count,
                          IF(installment > 0, 1, 0) installment_count
                  FROM    approvals
                  WHERE   business_id IS NOT NULL
                  AND     transacted_at between '2019-01-01' AND '2020-09-05'
          )
          GROUP BY business_id, issuer_name, timestamp
 ) GROUP BY business_id, timestamp

SELECT  DISTINCT
        business_id,
        registration_number,
        registration_code,
        status_code
FROM
(
      SELECT  COALESCE(b.business_id, l.business_id) AS business_id,
              COALESCE(b.registration_number, l.registration_number) AS registration_number,
              COALESCE(b.registration_code, '7') AS registration_code,
              CASE
                WHEN b.crefia_registered AND b.hometax_registered THEN '00'
                WHEN b.crefia_registered AND NOT b.hometax_registered THEN '01'
                WHEN NOT b.crefia_registered AND b.hometax_registered THEN '02'
                ELSE '03'
              END AS status_code
      FROM    (
              SELECT  business_id,
                      businesses.businesses.registration_number,
                      IF(businesses.businesses.created_at >= '2020-12-01', '1', '3') AS registration_code,
                      (
                        array_contains(businesses.credentials.types, 'Crefia')
                        OR array_contains(businesses.credentials.types, 'CrefiaBusiness')
                      ) AS crefia_registered,
                      (
                        array_contains(businesses.credentials.types, 'HometaxLogin')
                        OR array_contains(businesses.credentials.types, 'HometaxCertificate')
                      ) AS hometax_registered
              FROM    business_meta
      ) b FULL OUTER JOIN (
              SELECT   business_id,
                       registration_number
              FROM     last_sent_businesses
              WHERE    registration_code != '7'
      ) l ON b.registration_number = l.registration_number
) t
WHERE   t.business_id IS NOT NULL
AND     t.registration_number IS NOT NULL

        stats.last_year_3_month_avg_card_sales_amount,
        stats.last_year_6_month_avg_card_sales_count,
        CONCAT_WS('_', stats.location_meta.sido, stats.location_meta.sigungu, stats.location_meta.dong) AS address,
        CONCAT_WS('_', stats.classification_meta.depth_1_name, stats.classification_meta.depth_2_name, stats.classification_meta.depth_3_name) AS classification,
        CONCAT_WS(' ~ ', date_format(add_months('2021-01-01', -3), 'yyyyMMdd'), date_format(add_months('2021-01-01', -1), 'yyyyMMdd')) AS 3_month,
        CONCAT_WS(' ~ ', date_format(add_months('2021-01-01', -6), 'yyyyMMdd'), date_format(add_months('2021-01-01', -1), 'yyyyMMdd')) AS 6_month,
        CONCAT_WS(' ~ ', date_format(add_months('2021-01-01', -12), 'yyyyMMdd'), date_format(add_months('2021-01-01', -1), 'yyyyMMdd')) AS 12_month,
        CONCAT_WS(' ~ ', date_format(add_months('2021-01-01', -12), 'yyyyMMdd'), date_format(add_months('2021-01-01', -7), 'yyyyMMdd')) AS before_6_month,
        CONCAT_WS(' ~ ', date_format(add_months('2021-01-01', -15), 'yyyyMMdd'), date_format(add_months('2021-01-01', -13), 'yyyyMMdd')) AS last_year_3_month,
        CONCAT_WS(' ~ ', date_format(add_months('2021-01-01', -18), 'yyyyMMdd'), date_format(add_months('2021-01-01', -13), 'yyyyMMdd')) AS last_year_6_month
FROM (
    SELECT  business_id,
            MAX(location) as location_meta,
            MAX(classification) as classification_meta,
            SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -3), card_sales_amount, 0)) / SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -3), 1, 0)) AS 3_month_avg_card_sales_amount,
            SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -3), card_sales_amount, 0)) AS 3_month_sum_card_sales_amount,
            SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -3), returning_count, 0)) AS 3_month_sum_returning_count,
            SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -3), card_sales_count, 0)) AS 3_month_sum_card_sales_count,
            SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -3), card_sales_count, 0)) / SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -3), 1, 0)) AS 3_month_avg_card_sales_count,

            SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -6), card_sales_amount, 0)) AS 6_month_sum_card_sales_amount,
            SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -6), card_sales_amount, 0)) / SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -6), 1, 0)) AS 6_month_avg_card_sales_amount,
            SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -6), returning_count, 0)) AS 6_month_sum_returning_count,
            SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -6), card_sales_count, 0)) AS 6_month_sum_card_sales_count,
            SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -6), card_sales_count, 0)) / SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -6), 1, 0)) AS 6_month_avg_card_sales_count,

            SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -12), returning_count, 0)) / SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -12), 1, 0)) AS 12_month_avg_returning_count,
            SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -12) AND time < add_months('2021-01-01', -6), card_sales_amount, 0)) AS before_6_month_sum_card_sales_amount,
            SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -12) AND time < add_months('2021-01-01', -6), card_sales_amount, 0)) / SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -12) AND time < add_months('2021-01-01', -6), 1, 0)) AS before_6_month_avg_card_sales_amount,
            SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -12) AND time < add_months('2021-01-01', -6), card_sales_count, 0)) AS before_6_month_sum_card_sales_count,
            SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -12) AND time < add_months('2021-01-01', -6), card_sales_count, 0)) / SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -12) AND time < add_months('2021-01-01', -6), 1, 0)) AS before_6_month_avg_card_sales_count,

            SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -15) AND time < add_months('2021-01-01', -12), card_sales_amount, 0)) / SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -15) AND time < add_months('2021-01-01', -12), 1, 0)) AS last_year_3_month_avg_card_sales_amount,
            SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -18) AND time < add_months('2021-01-01', -12), card_sales_count, 0)) / SUM(IF (time >= add_months('2021-01-01', -18) AND time < add_months('2021-01-01', -12), 1, 0)) AS last_year_6_month_avg_card_sales_count
    FROM    transactions_stat_with_meta
    WHERE   time_unit = 'month'
    AND     time < '2021-01-01'
    GROUP BY 1
)   stats RIGHT OUTER JOIN business_meta_with_status meta
ON  stats.business_id = meta.business_id

SELECT  *,
        weekofyear(transacted_at_week) AS week_of_year
FROM    (
  SELECT  st.business_id,
          date_trunc('week', time) AS transacted_at_week,
          SUM(card_sales_amount) AS amount_sum,
          SUM(IF (hour(time) < 18 AND hour(time) >= 6, card_sales_amount, 0)) as day_time_amount_sum,
          SUM(IF (hour(time) >= 18 OR hour(time) < 6, card_sales_amount, 0)) as night_time_amount_sum,
          SUM(IF (weekday(time) > 4, card_sales_amount, 0)) as weekend_amount_sum,
          SUM(IF (weekday(time) <= 4, card_sales_amount, 0)) as weekday_amount_sum,
          SUM(card_sales_amount - returning_amount) as new_amount_sum,
          SUM(returning_amount) as revisit_amount_sum,
          SUM(card_sales_count) as tx_count,
          MAX(st.place.lot_address_1_depth) as lot_address_1_depth,
          MAX(st.place.lot_address_2_depth) as lot_address_2_depth,
          MAX(st.place.lot_address_3_depth) as lot_address_3_depth,
          MAX(st.place.kcd_classification_1_depth) as kcd_classification_1_depth,
          MAX(st.place.kcd_classification_2_depth) as kcd_classification_2_depth,
          MAX(st.place.kcd_classification_3_depth) as kcd_classification_3_depth
  FROM    transactions_stat_with_meta st, targets t
  WHERE   st.business_id = t.business_id
  AND     t.transacted_at_month_count = 13
  AND     st.time_unit = 'day_hour'
  AND     weekofyear(st.time) < weekofyear(current_date())
  GROUP BY 1, 2
)

SELECT  *,
        weekofyear(transacted_at_week) AS week_of_year
FROM    (
  SELECT  st.business_id,
          date_trunc('week', time) AS transacted_at_week,
          SUM(card_sales_amount) AS amount_sum,
          SUM(IF (hour(time) < 18, card_sales_amount, 0)) as day_time_amount_sum,
          SUM(IF (hour(time) >= 18, card_sales_amount, 0)) as night_time_amount_sum,
          SUM(IF (weekday(time) > 4, card_sales_amount, 0)) as weekend_amount_sum,
          SUM(IF (weekday(time) <= 4, card_sales_amount, 0)) as weekday_amount_sum,
          SUM(card_sales_amount - returning_amount) as new_amount_sum,
          SUM(returning_amount) as revisit_amount_sum,
          SUM(card_sales_count) as tx_count,
          MAX(st.place.lot_address_1_depth) as lot_address_1_depth,
          MAX(st.place.lot_address_2_depth) as lot_address_2_depth,
          MAX(st.place.lot_address_3_depth) as lot_address_3_depth,
          MAX(st.place.kcd_classification_1_depth) as kcd_classification_1_depth,
          MAX(st.place.kcd_classification_2_depth) as kcd_classification_2_depth,
          MAX(st.place.kcd_classification_3_depth) as kcd_classification_3_depth
  FROM    transactions_stat_with_meta st, targets t
  WHERE   st.business_id = t.business_id
  AND     t.transacted_at_month_count = 13
  AND     st.time_unit = 'day_hour'
  AND     weekofyear(st.time) < weekofyear(current_date())
  GROUP BY 1, 2
)

SELECT  /*+ BROADCAST(t) */
        src.*,
        location.sido AS sido,
        location.sigungu AS sigungu,
        location.dong AS dong,
        CASE
          WHEN classification.depth_1_name = '금융/보헙업' THEN '금융/보험업'
          ELSE classification.depth_1_name
        END AS classification_kcd_depth_1_name,
        CASE
          WHEN classification.depth_2_name = '금융/보헙업' THEN '금융/보험업'
          ELSE classification.depth_2_name
        END AS classification_kcd_depth_2_name
FROM    tx_with_meta_src src, (
  SELECT  *
  FROM    targets_src
  WHERE   transacted_at_month_count = 13
) t
WHERE   src.business_id = t.business_id
AND     classification.depth_1_name is not null
AND    (
   (
     time_unit = 'week' AND
     year(time) in (2019, 2020) AND
     weekofyear(time) < weekofyear(current_date()) AND
     weekofyear(time) >= weekofyear(current_date()) - 8
   ) OR
   (
     time_unit = 'day' AND
     time < current_date() AND
     time >= DATE_SUB(current_date(), 7)
   ) OR
   (
     time_unit = 'week' AND
     time >= to_date('2020-01-01', 'yyyy-MM-dd') AND time <= to_date('2020-07-12')
   ) OR
   (
     time_unit = 'day' AND
     time >= to_date('2020-01-01', 'yyyy-MM-dd') AND time <= to_date('2020-07-12')
   )
 )

WHERE   3_month_sum_card_sales_count > 0
GROUP BY 1

        AVG(6_month_sum_card_sales_count) AS classification_6_month_avg_card_sales_count
FROM    businesses_monthly_stats
WHERE   6_month_sum_card_sales_count > 0
GROUP BY 1

SELECT  stats.business_id,
        stats.registration_number,
        stats.registration_code,
        stats.status_code,
        date_format(date_sub('2021-01-01', 1), 'yyyyMMdd') as standard_date,
        CAST(3_month_avg_card_sales_amount AS bigint) AS TR0102_M03,
        3_month_sum_returning_count AS TR0251_M03,
        CAST((1 - 3_month_sum_returning_count / 3_month_sum_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS TR0260_M03,
        CAST((3_month_sum_returning_count / 3_month_sum_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS TR0261_M03,
        6_month_sum_returning_count AS TR0251_M06,
        CAST((1 - 6_month_sum_returning_count / 6_month_sum_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS TR0260_M06,
        CAST(12_month_avg_returning_count AS int) AS TR0256_M12,
        CAST((3_month_sum_card_sales_amount / 6_month_sum_card_sales_amount) * 100 AS int) AS TR4101_M03,
        CAST((3_month_avg_card_sales_amount / 6_month_avg_card_sales_amount) * 100 AS int) AS TR4102_M03,
        CAST((3_month_sum_card_sales_count / 6_month_sum_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS TR4201_M03,
        CAST((3_month_avg_card_sales_count / 6_month_avg_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS TR4202_M03,
        CAST((6_month_sum_card_sales_amount / before_6_month_sum_card_sales_amount) * 100 AS int) AS TR6101_M06,
        CAST((6_month_avg_card_sales_amount / before_6_month_avg_card_sales_amount) * 100 AS int) AS TR6102_M06,
        CAST((6_month_sum_card_sales_count / before_6_month_sum_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS TR6201_M06,
        CAST((6_month_avg_card_sales_count / before_6_month_avg_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS TR6202_M06,
        CAST((3_month_avg_card_sales_amount / last_year_3_month_avg_card_sales_amount) * 100 AS int) AS TR7102_M03,
        CAST((6_month_avg_card_sales_count / last_year_6_month_avg_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS TR7202_M06,
        CAST((3_month_sum_card_sales_count / address_3_month_avg_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS LT8201_M03,
        CAST((6_month_sum_card_sales_amount / classification_6_month_avg_card_sales_amount) * 100 AS int) AS CL8101_M06,
        CAST((6_month_sum_card_sales_count / classification_6_month_avg_card_sales_count) * 100 AS int) AS CL8201_M06,
        CAST((3_month_avg_hometax_sales_amount / 12_month_avg_hometax_sales_amount) * 100 AS int) AS SL5102_M03
FROM businesses_monthly_stats stats
LEFT OUTER JOIN address_monthly_stats ON stats.address = address_monthly_stats.address
LEFT OUTER JOIN classification_monthly_stats classification ON stats.classification = classification.classification
LEFT OUTER JOIN hometax_sales_monthly_stat hometax_stats ON stats.business_id = hometax_stats.business_id

SELECT
